35 COutputLegacy::COutputLegacy(CConfig *config) {
36 
37  rank = SU2_MPI::GetRank();
38  size = SU2_MPI::GetSize();
39 
40  unsigned short iDim, iSpan, iMarker;
41 
42  /*--- Initialize point and connectivity counters to zero. ---*/
43 
44  /*--- Initialize turbo flag ---*/
45  turbo = config->GetBoolTurbomachinery();
46 
47  if(turbo){
48  /*--- Initializate quantities for turboperformace ---*/
49  nSpanWiseSections = config->GetnSpanMaxAllZones();
50  nMarkerTurboPerf = config->GetnMarker_TurboPerformance();
51 
52 
53  TotalStaticEfficiency = new su2double*[nMarkerTurboPerf];
54  TotalTotalEfficiency = new su2double*[nMarkerTurboPerf];
55  KineticEnergyLoss = new su2double*[nMarkerTurboPerf];
56  TRadius = new su2double*[nMarkerTurboPerf];

90  TemperatureIn = new su2double*[nMarkerTurboPerf];
91  TemperatureOut = new su2double*[nMarkerTurboPerf];
92  TotalPressureIn = new su2double*[nMarkerTurboPerf];
93  TotalPressureOut = new su2double*[nMarkerTurboPerf];
94  TotalTemperatureOut = new su2double*[nMarkerTurboPerf];
95  EnthalpyIn = new su2double*[nMarkerTurboPerf];

102 
103  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarkerTurboPerf; iMarker++){
104  TotalStaticEfficiency [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
105  TotalTotalEfficiency [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
106  KineticEnergyLoss [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
107  TRadius [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
108  TotalPressureLoss [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];

115  TotalEnthalpyIn [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
116  TotalEnthalpyIn_BC [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
117  EntropyIn [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
118  EntropyOut [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
119  EntropyIn_BC [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
120  PressureRatio [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
121  TotalTemperatureIn [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
122  EnthalpyOut [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
123  MachIn [iMarker] = new su2double*[nSpanWiseSections + 1];
124  MachOut [iMarker] = new su2double*[nSpanWiseSections + 1];
125  VelocityOutIs [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
126  DensityIn [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
127  PressureIn [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
128  TurboVelocityIn [iMarker] = new su2double*[nSpanWiseSections + 1];
129  DensityOut [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
130  PressureOut [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
131  TurboVelocityOut [iMarker] = new su2double*[nSpanWiseSections + 1];

148  Turb2LamViscRatioIn [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
149  TurbIntensityOut [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
150  Turb2LamViscRatioOut [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
151  NuFactorIn [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
152  NuFactorOut [iMarker] = new su2double [nSpanWiseSections + 1];
153 
154 
155  for (iSpan = 0; iSpan < nSpanWiseSections + 1; iSpan++){
156  TotalStaticEfficiency [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
157  TotalTotalEfficiency [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
158  KineticEnergyLoss [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
159  TRadius [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
160  TotalPressureLoss [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
161  MassFlowIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
162  MassFlowOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
163  FlowAngleIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
164  FlowAngleIn_BC [iMarker][iSpan] = config->GetFlowAngleIn_BC();
165  FlowAngleOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
166  EulerianWork [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
167  TotalEnthalpyIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
168  TotalEnthalpyIn_BC [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
169  EntropyIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
170  EntropyOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
171  EntropyIn_BC [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
172  PressureRatio [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
173  TotalTemperatureIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
174  EnthalpyOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
175 
176 
177  VelocityOutIs [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
178  DensityIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
179  PressureIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
180 
181  DensityOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
182  PressureOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
183 
184  EnthalpyOutIs [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
185  EntropyGen [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
186  AbsFlowAngleIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
187  TotalEnthalpyOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
188  TotalEnthalpyOutIs [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
189  RothalpyIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
190  RothalpyOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
191  AbsFlowAngleOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
192  PressureOut_BC [iMarker][iSpan] = config->GetPressureOut_BC();
193 
194  TemperatureIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
195  TemperatureOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
196  TotalPressureIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
197  TotalPressureOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
198  TotalTemperatureOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
199  EnthalpyIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
200  TurbIntensityIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
201  Turb2LamViscRatioIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
202  TurbIntensityOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
203  Turb2LamViscRatioOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
204  NuFactorIn [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
205  NuFactorOut [iMarker][iSpan] = 0.0;
206  MachIn [iMarker][iSpan] = new su2double[4];
207  MachOut [iMarker][iSpan] = new su2double[4];
208  TurboVelocityIn [iMarker][iSpan] = new su2double[4];
209  TurboVelocityOut [iMarker][iSpan] = new su2double[4];
210 
211  for (iDim = 0; iDim < 4; iDim++){
212  MachIn [iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = 0.0;
213  MachOut [iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = 0.0;
214  TurboVelocityIn [iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = 0.0;
215  TurboVelocityOut [iMarker][iSpan][iDim] = 0.0;
216  }
217  }
218  }
219  }

222 COutputLegacy::~COutputLegacy(void) {
223  /* delete pointers initialized at construction*/
224  /* Coords and Conn_*(Connectivity) have their own dealloc functions */
225  /* Data is taken care of in DeallocateSolution function */
226 
227  /*--- Delete turboperformance pointers initiliazed at constrction ---*/
228  unsigned short iMarker, iSpan;
229  if(turbo){
230  for(iMarker = 0; iMarker< nMarkerTurboPerf; iMarker++){
231  for(iSpan=0; iSpan<nSpanWiseSections+1; iSpan++){
232  delete [] MachIn [iMarker][iSpan];
233  delete [] MachOut [iMarker][iSpan];
234  delete [] TurboVelocityIn [iMarker][iSpan];
235  delete [] TurboVelocityOut[iMarker][iSpan];
236  }
237  }
238  for(iMarker = 0; iMarker< nMarkerTurboPerf; iMarker++){
239  delete [] TotalStaticEfficiency[iMarker];
240  delete [] TotalTotalEfficiency [iMarker];
241  delete [] KineticEnergyLoss [iMarker];
242  delete [] TRadius [iMarker];
243  delete [] TotalPressureLoss [iMarker];
244  delete [] MassFlowIn [iMarker];
245  delete [] MassFlowOut [iMarker];
246  delete [] FlowAngleIn [iMarker];
247  delete [] FlowAngleOut [iMarker];
248  delete [] EulerianWork [iMarker];
249  delete [] TotalEnthalpyIn [iMarker];
250  delete [] TotalEnthalpyOut [iMarker];
251  delete [] TotalEnthalpyOutIs [iMarker];
252  delete [] PressureRatio [iMarker];
253  delete [] EnthalpyOut [iMarker];
254  delete [] VelocityOutIs [iMarker];
255  delete [] TotalTemperatureIn [iMarker];
256  delete [] FlowAngleIn_BC [iMarker];
257  delete [] EntropyIn [iMarker];
258  delete [] EntropyIn_BC [iMarker];
259  delete [] EntropyOut [iMarker];
260  delete [] TotalEnthalpyIn_BC [iMarker];
261  delete [] DensityIn [iMarker];
262  delete [] PressureIn [iMarker];
263  delete [] DensityOut [iMarker];
264  delete [] PressureOut [iMarker];
265  delete [] EnthalpyOutIs [iMarker];
266  delete [] EntropyGen [iMarker];
267  delete [] AbsFlowAngleIn [iMarker];
268  delete [] RothalpyIn [iMarker];
269  delete [] RothalpyOut [iMarker];
270  delete [] AbsFlowAngleOut [iMarker];
271  delete [] PressureOut_BC [iMarker];
272  delete [] MachIn [iMarker];
273  delete [] MachOut [iMarker];
274  delete [] TurboVelocityIn [iMarker];
275  delete [] TurboVelocityOut [iMarker];
276  delete [] TemperatureIn [iMarker];
277  delete [] TemperatureOut [iMarker];
278  delete [] TotalPressureIn [iMarker];
279  delete [] TotalPressureOut [iMarker];
280  delete [] TotalTemperatureOut [iMarker];
281  delete [] EnthalpyIn [iMarker];
282  delete [] TurbIntensityIn [iMarker];
283  delete [] Turb2LamViscRatioIn [iMarker];
284  delete [] TurbIntensityOut [iMarker];
285  delete [] Turb2LamViscRatioOut [iMarker];
286  delete [] NuFactorIn [iMarker];
287  delete [] NuFactorOut [iMarker];
288 
289 
290  }

343 void COutputLegacy::SetConvHistory_Header(ofstream *ConvHist_file, CConfig *config, unsigned short val_iZone, unsigned short val_iInst) {
344  char cstr[200], turb_resid[1000], adj_turb_resid[1000];
345  unsigned short iMarker_Monitoring;
346  string Monitoring_Tag, monitoring_coeff, aeroelastic_coeff, turbo_coeff;
347 
348  bool rotating_frame = config->GetRotating_Frame();
349  bool aeroelastic = config->GetAeroelastic_Simulation();
350  bool equiv_area = config->GetEquivArea();
351  bool buffet = (config->GetViscous() || config->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::COMPRESSIBLE);
352  bool engine = ((config->GetnMarker_EngineInflow() != 0) || (config->GetnMarker_EngineExhaust() != 0));
353  bool actuator_disk = ((config->GetnMarker_ActDiskInlet() != 0) || (config->GetnMarker_ActDiskOutlet() != 0));
354  bool turbulent = ((config->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::RANS) || (config->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::ADJ_RANS) ||
355  (config->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_RANS) || (config->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_INC_RANS) ||
356  (config->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::INC_RANS));
357  bool cont_adj = config->GetContinuous_Adjoint();
358  bool disc_adj = config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint();
359  bool frozen_visc = (cont_adj && config->GetFrozen_Visc_Cont()) ||( disc_adj && config->GetFrozen_Visc_Disc());
360  bool inv_design = (config->GetInvDesign_Cp() || config->GetInvDesign_HeatFlux());
361 
362  bool output_surface = (config->GetnMarker_Analyze() != 0);
363  bool output_comboObj = (config->GetnObj() > 1);
364  bool output_per_surface = true;
365  bool turbo = config->GetBoolTurbomachinery();
366  unsigned short direct_diff = config->GetDirectDiff();
367 
368  bool compressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::COMPRESSIBLE);
369  bool incompressible = (config->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::INCOMPRESSIBLE);
370  bool incload = config->GetIncrementalLoad();
371 
372  bool thermal = false; /* Flag for whether to print heat flux values */
373  bool weakly_coupled_heat = config->GetWeakly_Coupled_Heat();
374  bool radiation = config->AddRadiation();
375 
376  if (config->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::RANS || config->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::NAVIER_STOKES ||
377  config->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::INC_RANS || config->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::INC_NAVIER_STOKES) {
378  thermal = true;
379  }
380 
381  /*--- Write file name with extension ---*/
382  string filename = config->GetConv_FileName();
383  string hist_ext = ".csv";
384  if (config->GetTabular_FileFormat() == TAB_OUTPUT::TAB_TECPLOT) hist_ext = ".dat";
385 
386  if(config->GetnZone() > 1){
387  filename = config->GetMultizone_HistoryFileName(filename, val_iZone, hist_ext);
388  }
389  if(config->GetnTimeInstances() > 1){
390  filename = config->GetMultiInstance_HistoryFileName(filename, val_iInst);
391  }
392 
393  if (config->GetTime_Domain() && config->GetRestart()) {
394  filename = config->GetUnsteady_FileName(filename, config->GetRestart_Iter(), hist_ext);
395  }
396 
397  strcpy (cstr, filename.data());
398 
399  ConvHist_file->open(cstr, ios::out);
400  ConvHist_file->precision(15);
401 
402  /*--- Begin of the header ---*/
403 
404  char begin[]= "\"Iteration\"";
405 
406  /*--- Header for the coefficients ---*/
407 
408  char flow_coeff[]= ",\"CL\",\"CD\",\"CSF\",\"CMx\",\"CMy\",\"CMz\",\"CFx\",\"CFy\",\"CFz\",\"CL/CD\",\"AoA\",\"Custom_ObjFunc\"";
409  char heat_coeff[]= ",\"HeatFlux_Total\",\"HeatFlux_Maximum\",\"Temperature_Total\"";
410  char equivalent_area_coeff[]= ",\"CEquivArea\",\"CNearFieldOF\"";
411  char buffet_coeff[]= ",\"Buffet_Metric\"";
412  char engine_coeff[]= ",\"NetThrust\",\"Power\",\"AeroCDrag\",\"SolidCDrag\",\"Radial_Distortion\",\"Circumferential_Distortion\"";
413  char rotating_frame_coeff[]= ",\"CMerit\",\"CT\",\"CQ\"";
414  char fem_coeff[]= ",\"VM_Stress\",\"Force_Coeff\"";
415  char fem_incload[]= ",\"IncLoad\"";
416  char adj_coeff[]= ",\"Sens_Geo\",\"Sens_Mach\",\"Sens_AoA\",\"Sens_Press\",\"Sens_Temp\",\"Sens_AoS\"";
417  char adj_inc_coeff[]=",\"Sens_Geo\",\"Sens_Vin\",\"Sens_Pout\",\"Sens_Temp\"";
418  char adj_turbo_coeff[]=",\"Sens_Geo\",\"Sens_PressOut\",\"Sens_TotTempIn\"";
419  char surface_outputs[]= ",\"Avg_MassFlow\",\"Avg_Mach\",\"Avg_Temp\",\"Avg_Press\",\"Avg_Density\",\"Avg_Enthalpy\",\"Avg_NormalVel\",\"Uniformity\",\"Secondary_Strength\",\"Momentum_Distortion\",\"Secondary_Over_Uniformity\",\"Avg_TotalTemp\",\"Avg_TotalPress\",\"Pressure_Drop\"";
420  char Cp_inverse_design[]= ",\"Cp_Diff\"";
421  char Heat_inverse_design[]= ",\"HeatFlux_Diff\"";
422  char d_flow_coeff[] = ",\"D(CL)\",\"D(CD)\",\"D(CSF)\",\"D(CMx)\",\"D(CMy)\",\"D(CMz)\",\"D(CFx)\",\"D(CFy)\",\"D(CFz)\",\"D(CL/CD)\",\"D(Custom_ObjFunc)\"";
423  char d_thermal_coeff[] = ",\"D(HeatFlux_Total)\",\"D(HeatFlux_Maximum)\"";
424  char d_engine[] = ",\"D(NetThrust)\",\"D(Power)\",\"D(AeroCDrag)\",\"D(SolidCDrag)\",\"D(Radial_Distortion)\",\"D(Circumferential_Distortion)\"";
425  char d_turbo_coeff[] = ",\"D(TotalPressureLoss_0)\",\"D(FlowAngleOut_0)\",\"D(TotalEfficency)\",\"D(TotalStaticEfficiency)\", \"D(EntropyGen)\"";
426  char d_surface_outputs[]= ",\"D(Uniformity)\",\"D(Secondary_Strength)\",\"D(Momentum_Distortion)\",\"D(Secondary_Over_Uniformity)\",\"D(Pressure_Drop)\"";
427 
428  /*--- Find the markers being monitored and create a header for them ---*/
429 
430  for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_Monitoring(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
431  Monitoring_Tag = config->GetMarker_Monitoring_TagBound(iMarker_Monitoring);
432  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CL_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
433  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CD_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
434  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CSF_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
435  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CL/CD_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
436  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CFx_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
437  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CFy_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
438  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CFz_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
439  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CMx_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
440  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CMy_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
441  monitoring_coeff += ",\"CMz_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
442  if(buffet) monitoring_coeff += ",\"Buffet_Metric_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
443  aeroelastic_coeff += ",\"plunge_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
444  aeroelastic_coeff += ",\"pitch_" + Monitoring_Tag + "\"";
445  }
446 
447  if (turbo){
448  for (iMarker_Monitoring = 0; iMarker_Monitoring < config->GetnMarker_TurboPerformance(); iMarker_Monitoring++) {
449 
450  stringstream tag;
451  tag << iMarker_Monitoring + 1;
452 
453  turbo_coeff += ",\"TotalPressureLoss_" + tag.str() + "\"";
454  turbo_coeff += ",\"KineticEnergyLoss_" + tag.str() + "\"";
455  turbo_coeff += ",\"EntropyGen_" + tag.str() + "\"";
456  turbo_coeff += ",\"EulerianWork_" + tag.str() + "\"";
457  turbo_coeff += ",\"PressureRatio_" + tag.str() + "\"";
458  turbo_coeff += ",\"FlowAngleIn_" + tag.str() + "\"";
459  turbo_coeff += ",\"FlowAngleOut_" + tag.str() + "\"";
460  turbo_coeff += ",\"AbsFlowAngleIn_" + tag.str() + "\"";
461  turbo_coeff += ",\"AbsFlowAngleOut_" + tag.str() + "\"";
462  turbo_coeff += ",\"MassFlowIn_" + tag.str() + "\"";
463  turbo_coeff += ",\"MassFlowOut_" + tag.str() + "\"";
464  turbo_coeff += ",\"MachIn_" + tag.str() + "\"";
465  turbo_coeff += ",\"MachOut_" + tag.str() + "\"";
466  // different from zero only in multi-zone computation
467  turbo_coeff += ",\"TotalEfficiency_" + tag.str() + "\"";
468  turbo_coeff += ",\"TotalStaticEfficiency_" + tag.str() + "\"";
469 
470  }
471  }
472 
473  char combo_obj[] = ",\"ComboObj\"";
474 
475  /*--- Header for the residuals ---*/
476 
477  char flow_resid[]= ",\"Res_Flow[0]\",\"Res_Flow[1]\",\"Res_Flow[2]\",\"Res_Flow[3]\",\"Res_Flow[4]\"";
478  char adj_flow_resid[]= ",\"Res_AdjFlow[0]\",\"Res_AdjFlow[1]\",\"Res_AdjFlow[2]\",\"Res_AdjFlow[3]\",\"Res_AdjFlow[4]\"";
479  switch (config->GetKind_Turb_Model()) {
480  case TURB_MODEL::SA:
481  SPRINTF (turb_resid, ",\"Res_Turb[0]\"");
482  break;
483  case TURB_MODEL::SST:
484  SPRINTF (turb_resid, ",\"Res_Turb[0]\",\"Res_Turb[1]\"");
485  break;
486  default: break;
487  }
488  switch (config->GetKind_Turb_Model()) {
489  case TURB_MODEL::SA:
490  SPRINTF (adj_turb_resid, ",\"Res_AdjTurb[0]\"");
491  break;
492  case TURB_MODEL::SST:
493  SPRINTF (adj_turb_resid, ",\"Res_AdjTurb[0]\",\"Res_AdjTurb[1]\"");
494  break;
495  default: break;
496  }
497  char fem_resid[]= ",\"Res_FEM[0]\",\"Res_FEM[1]\",\"Res_FEM[2]\"";
498  char heat_resid[]= ",\"Res_Heat\"";
499  char rad_resid[]= ",\"Res_P1-rad\"";
500 
501  /*--- End of the header ---*/
502 
503  char end[]= ",\"Linear_Solver_Iterations\",\"CFL_Number\",\"Time(min)\"\n";
504  char endfea[]= ",\"Linear_Solver_Iterations\",\"Time(min)\"\n";
505 
506  if ((config->GetTabular_FileFormat() == TAB_OUTPUT::TAB_TECPLOT)) {
507  ConvHist_file[0] << "TITLE = \"SU2 Simulation\"" << endl;
508  ConvHist_file[0] << "VARIABLES = ";
509  }
510 
511  /*--- Write the header, case depending ---*/
512 
513  switch (config->GetKind_Solver()) {
514 
515  case MAIN_SOLVER::EULER : case MAIN_SOLVER::NAVIER_STOKES: case MAIN_SOLVER::RANS :
516  case MAIN_SOLVER::INC_EULER : case MAIN_SOLVER::INC_NAVIER_STOKES: case MAIN_SOLVER::INC_RANS :
517  case MAIN_SOLVER::FEM_EULER : case MAIN_SOLVER::FEM_NAVIER_STOKES: case MAIN_SOLVER::FEM_RANS : case MAIN_SOLVER::FEM_LES:
518  ConvHist_file[0] << begin;
519  if (!turbo) ConvHist_file[0] << flow_coeff;
520  if (buffet) ConvHist_file[0] << buffet_coeff;
521  if (turbo) ConvHist_file[0] << turbo_coeff;
522  if (thermal && !turbo) ConvHist_file[0] << heat_coeff;
523  if (equiv_area) ConvHist_file[0] << equivalent_area_coeff;
524  if (engine || actuator_disk) ConvHist_file[0] << engine_coeff;
525  if (inv_design) {
526  ConvHist_file[0] << Cp_inverse_design;
527  if (thermal && !turbo) ConvHist_file[0] << Heat_inverse_design;
528  }
529  if (rotating_frame && !turbo) ConvHist_file[0] << rotating_frame_coeff;
530 
531  ConvHist_file[0] << flow_resid;
532  if (turbulent) ConvHist_file[0] << turb_resid;
533  if (weakly_coupled_heat) ConvHist_file[0] << heat_resid;
534  if (radiation) ConvHist_file[0] << rad_resid;
535  if (aeroelastic) ConvHist_file[0] << aeroelastic_coeff;
536  if (output_per_surface) ConvHist_file[0] << monitoring_coeff;
537  if (output_surface) ConvHist_file[0] << surface_outputs;
538  if (direct_diff != NO_DERIVATIVE) {
539  if (!turbo) ConvHist_file[0] << d_flow_coeff;
540  else ConvHist_file[0] << d_turbo_coeff;
541  if (engine || actuator_disk) ConvHist_file[0] << d_engine;
542  if (thermal) ConvHist_file[0] << d_thermal_coeff;
543  if (output_surface) ConvHist_file[0] << d_surface_outputs;
544  }
545  if (output_comboObj) ConvHist_file[0] << combo_obj;
546  ConvHist_file[0] << end;
547 
548  break;
549 
550  case MAIN_SOLVER::ADJ_EULER : case MAIN_SOLVER::ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES : case MAIN_SOLVER::ADJ_RANS:
551  case MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_EULER: case MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES: case MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_RANS:
552  case MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_INC_EULER: case MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_INC_NAVIER_STOKES: case MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_INC_RANS:
553  if (!turbo) {
554  if (compressible) {
555  ConvHist_file[0] << begin << adj_coeff << adj_flow_resid;
556  }
557  if (incompressible) {
558  ConvHist_file[0] << begin << adj_inc_coeff << adj_flow_resid;
559  }
560  }
561  else ConvHist_file[0] << begin << adj_turbo_coeff << adj_flow_resid;
562  if ((turbulent) && (!frozen_visc)) ConvHist_file[0] << adj_turb_resid;
563  ConvHist_file[0] << end;
564  break;
565 
566  case MAIN_SOLVER::HEAT_EQUATION:
567  ConvHist_file[0] << begin << heat_coeff;
568  ConvHist_file[0] << heat_resid << end;
569  break;
570 
571  case MAIN_SOLVER::FEM_ELASTICITY:
572  ConvHist_file[0] << begin << fem_coeff;
573  if (incload) ConvHist_file[0] << fem_incload;
574  ConvHist_file[0] << fem_resid << endfea;
575  break;
576 
577  case MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_FEM:
578  ConvHist_file[0] << begin << fem_coeff;
579  ConvHist_file[0] << fem_resid << endfea;
580  break;
581 
582  default:
583  break;
584  }
585 
586  if (config->GetTabular_FileFormat() == TAB_OUTPUT::TAB_TECPLOT) {
587  ConvHist_file[0] << "ZONE T= \"Convergence history\"" << endl;
588  }
589 
590 }
591 
592 
593 void COutputLegacy::SetConvHistory_Body(ofstream *ConvHist_file,
594  CGeometry ****geometry,
595  CSolver *****solver_container,
596  CConfig **config,
597  CIntegration ****integration,
598  bool DualTime_Iteration,
599  su2double timeused,
600  unsigned short val_iZone,
601  unsigned short val_iInst) {
602 
603  bool output_surface = (config[val_iZone]->GetnMarker_Analyze() != 0);
604  bool output_comboObj = (config[val_iZone]->GetnObj() > 1);
605  bool fluid_structure = (config[val_iZone]->GetFSI_Simulation());
606  bool fea = ((config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver()== MAIN_SOLVER::FEM_ELASTICITY)||(config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver()== MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_FEM));
607  unsigned long iIntIter = config[val_iZone]->GetInnerIter();
608  unsigned long iExtIter = config[val_iZone]->GetInnerIter();
609  unsigned short FinestMesh = config[val_iZone]->GetFinestMesh();
610  unsigned short nZone = config[val_iZone]->GetnZone();
611  unsigned short nInst = config[val_iZone]->GetnTimeInstances();
612  bool cont_adj = config[val_iZone]->GetContinuous_Adjoint();
613  bool disc_adj = config[val_iZone]->GetDiscrete_Adjoint();
614  bool energy = config[val_iZone]->GetEnergy_Equation();
615  bool incload = config[val_iZone]->GetIncrementalLoad();
616  bool fixed_cl = config[val_iZone]->GetFixed_CL_Mode();
617  bool output_files = true;
618 
619  bool radiation = config[val_iZone]->AddRadiation();
620 
621  bool compressible = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::COMPRESSIBLE);
622  bool incompressible = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::INCOMPRESSIBLE);
623 
624  if (!disc_adj && !cont_adj && !DualTime_Iteration) {
625 
626  if (fixed_cl &&
627  (solver_container[val_iZone][val_iInst][MESH_0][FLOW_SOL]->GetStart_AoA_FD()) &&
628  (iExtIter != solver_container[val_iZone][val_iInst][MESH_0][FLOW_SOL]->GetIter_Update_AoA())) {
629  output_files = false;
630  }
631 
632  if (fea || fluid_structure) output_files = false;
633 
634  /*--- We need to evaluate some of the objective functions to write the value on the history file ---*/
635 
636  if (((iExtIter % (config[val_iZone]->GetVolumeOutputFrequency(0) )) == 0) ||
637  (!fixed_cl && (iExtIter == (config[val_iZone]->GetnInner_Iter()-1))) ||
638  /*--- If CL mode we need to compute the complete solution at two very particular iterations ---*/
639  (fixed_cl && (iExtIter == (config[val_iZone]->GetnInner_Iter()-2) ||
640  (solver_container[val_iZone][val_iInst][MESH_0][FLOW_SOL]->GetStart_AoA_FD() &&
641  iExtIter == solver_container[val_iZone][val_iInst][MESH_0][FLOW_SOL]->GetIter_Update_AoA())))) {
642 
643 
644  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && output_files) cout << endl << "------------------------ Evaluate Special Output ------------------------";
645 
646  switch (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver()) {
647 
648  case MAIN_SOLVER::EULER: case MAIN_SOLVER::NAVIER_STOKES: case MAIN_SOLVER::RANS:
649  case MAIN_SOLVER::INC_EULER: case MAIN_SOLVER::INC_NAVIER_STOKES: case MAIN_SOLVER::INC_RANS:
650  /*--- For specific applications, evaluate and plot the surface. ---*/
651 
652  if (config[val_iZone]->GetnMarker_Analyze() != 0) {
653  SpecialOutput_AnalyzeSurface(solver_container[val_iZone][val_iInst][MESH_0][FLOW_SOL],
654  geometry[val_iZone][val_iInst][MESH_0], config[val_iZone], output_files);
655  }
656 
657  /*--- For specific applications, evaluate and plot the surface. ---*/
658 
659  if ((config[val_iZone]->GetnMarker_Analyze() != 0) && compressible) {
660  SpecialOutput_Distortion(solver_container[val_iZone][val_iInst][MESH_0][FLOW_SOL],
661  geometry[val_iZone][val_iInst][MESH_0], config[val_iZone], output_files);
662  }
663 
664  /*--- For specific applications, evaluate and plot the cp coefficent at different stations. ---*/
665 
666  if (config[val_iZone]->GetPlot_Section_Forces()) {
667  SpecialOutput_SpanLoad(solver_container[val_iZone][val_iInst][MESH_0][FLOW_SOL],
668  geometry[val_iZone][val_iInst][MESH_0], config[val_iZone], output_files);
669  }
670 
671  break;
672 
673  default:
674  break;
675  }
676 
677  /*--- Output a file with the forces breakdown. ---*/
678 
679  if (config[val_iZone]->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::HARMONIC_BALANCE) {
680  SpecialOutput_HarmonicBalance(solver_container, geometry, config, val_iInst, nInst, output_files);
681  }
682 
683  /*--- Compute span-wise values file for turbomachinery. ---*/
684 
685  if (config[val_iZone]->GetBoolTurbomachinery()) {
686  SpecialOutput_Turbo(solver_container, geometry, config, val_iZone, output_files);
687  }
688 
689  /*--- Output a file with the forces breakdown. ---*/
690 
691  SpecialOutput_ForcesBreakdown(solver_container, geometry, config, val_iZone, output_files);
692 
693  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && output_files) cout << "-------------------------------------------------------------------------" << endl << endl;
694 
695  }
696 
697  }
698 
699  /*--- Output using only the master node ---*/
700 
701  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
702 
703  /*-- Compute the total objective if a "combo" objective is used ---*/
704 
705  if (output_comboObj) {
706  switch (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver()) {
707  case MAIN_SOLVER::EULER: case MAIN_SOLVER::NAVIER_STOKES: case MAIN_SOLVER::RANS:
708  case MAIN_SOLVER::INC_EULER: case MAIN_SOLVER::INC_NAVIER_STOKES: case MAIN_SOLVER::INC_RANS:
709  solver_container[val_iZone][val_iInst][FinestMesh][FLOW_SOL]->Evaluate_ObjFunc(config[val_iZone],
710  solver_container[val_iZone][val_iInst][FinestMesh]);
711  break;
712  default:
713  break;
714  }
715  }
716 
717  unsigned long ExtIter_OffSet = config[val_iZone]->GetExtIter_OffSet();
718  if (config[val_iZone]->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_1ST ||
719  config[val_iZone]->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::DT_STEPPING_2ND)
720  ExtIter_OffSet = 0;
721 
722  /*--- WARNING: These buffers have hard-coded lengths. Note that you
723  may have to adjust them to be larger if adding more entries. ---*/
724 
725  char begin[1000], direct_coeff[1000], heat_coeff[1000], equivalent_area_coeff[1000], engine_coeff[1000], rotating_frame_coeff[1000], Cp_inverse_design[1000], Heat_inverse_design[1000], surface_coeff[1000], aeroelastic_coeff[1000], monitoring_coeff[10000], buffet_coeff[1000],
726  adjoint_coeff[1000], flow_resid[1000], adj_flow_resid[1000], turb_resid[1000], trans_resid[1000],
727  adj_turb_resid[1000], rad_resid[1000],
728  begin_fem[1000], fem_coeff[1000], heat_resid[1000], combo_obj[1000],
729  fem_resid[1000], end[1000], end_fem[1000], surface_outputs[1000], d_surface_outputs[1000], d_direct_coeff[1000], turbo_coeff[10000];
730 
731 
732  su2double dummy = 0.0;
733  const su2double *Coord = nullptr;
734  unsigned short iVar, iMarker_Monitoring;
735 
736  unsigned long LinSolvIter = 0, iPointMaxResid;
737  su2double timeiter = timeused/su2double(iExtIter+1);
738 
739  unsigned short nDim = geometry[val_iZone][val_iInst][FinestMesh]->GetnDim();
740 
741 
742  bool rotating_frame = config[val_iZone]->GetRotating_Frame();
743  bool aeroelastic = config[val_iZone]->GetAeroelastic_Simulation();
744  bool equiv_area = config[val_iZone]->GetEquivArea();
745  bool engine = ((config[val_iZone]->GetnMarker_EngineInflow() != 0) || (config[val_iZone]->GetnMarker_EngineExhaust() != 0));
746  bool actuator_disk = ((config[val_iZone]->GetnMarker_ActDiskInlet() != 0) || (config[val_iZone]->GetnMarker_ActDiskOutlet() != 0));
747  bool inv_design = (config[val_iZone]->GetInvDesign_Cp() || config[val_iZone]->GetInvDesign_HeatFlux());
748  bool transition = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Trans_Model() == TURB_TRANS_MODEL::LM);
749  bool thermal = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::RANS || config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::NAVIER_STOKES ||
750  config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::INC_NAVIER_STOKES || config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::INC_RANS );
751  bool turbulent = ((config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::RANS) || (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::ADJ_RANS) ||
752  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_RANS) || config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::INC_RANS ||
753  config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_INC_RANS);
754  bool adjoint = cont_adj || disc_adj;
755  bool frozen_visc = (cont_adj && config[val_iZone]->GetFrozen_Visc_Cont()) ||( disc_adj && config[val_iZone]->GetFrozen_Visc_Disc());
756  bool heat = ((config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::HEAT_EQUATION) || (config[val_iZone]->GetWeakly_Coupled_Heat()));
757  bool weakly_coupled_heat = config[val_iZone]->GetWeakly_Coupled_Heat();
758  bool flow = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::EULER) || (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::NAVIER_STOKES) ||
759  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::RANS) || (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::FEM_EULER) ||
760  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::FEM_NAVIER_STOKES) || (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::FEM_RANS) ||
761  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::FEM_LES) || (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::ADJ_EULER) ||
762  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::ADJ_NAVIER_STOKES) || (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::ADJ_RANS) ||
763  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::INC_EULER) || (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::INC_NAVIER_STOKES) ||
764  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::INC_RANS);
765  bool buffet = (config[val_iZone]->GetViscous() || config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::COMPRESSIBLE);
766 
767  bool fem = ((config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::FEM_ELASTICITY) || // FEM structural solver.
768  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_FEM));
769  bool linear_analysis = (config[val_iZone]->GetGeometricConditions() == STRUCT_DEFORMATION::SMALL);
770  bool nonlinear_analysis = (config[val_iZone]->GetGeometricConditions() == STRUCT_DEFORMATION::LARGE);
771  bool fsi = (config[val_iZone]->GetFSI_Simulation());
772  bool discadj_fem = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_FEM);
773 
774  bool turbo = config[val_iZone]->GetBoolTurbomachinery();
775 
776  unsigned short nTurboPerf = config[val_iZone]->GetnMarker_TurboPerformance();
777 
778  bool output_per_surface = true;
779 
780  unsigned short direct_diff = config[val_iZone]->GetDirectDiff();
781 
782  long ExtraHeatOutputZone = config[val_iZone]->GetExtraHeatOutputZone() - 1;
783  bool extra_heat_output = false;
784  su2double Extra_Total_Heat = 0.0;
785  //su2double Extra_Total_Temperature = 0.0;
786  su2double Extra_Heat_Residual = 0.0;
787 
788  if (ExtraHeatOutputZone > -1) {
789  if (ExtraHeatOutputZone > nZone) {
790  SU2_MPI::Error("Error in output routine: Extra output zone number exceeds total number of zones.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
791  }
792  else if ((config[ExtraHeatOutputZone]->GetKind_Solver() != MAIN_SOLVER::HEAT_EQUATION)) {
793  SU2_MPI::Error("Error in output routine: No heat solver in extra output zone.", CURRENT_FUNCTION);
794  }
795  else {
796  extra_heat_output = true;
797  }
798  }
799 
800  /*--- Initialize variables to store information from all domains (direct solution) ---*/
801 
802  su2double Total_CL = 0.0, Total_CD = 0.0, Total_CSF = 0.0, Total_CMx = 0.0, Total_CMy = 0.0, Total_CMz = 0.0, Total_CEff = 0.0,
803  Total_CEquivArea = 0.0, Total_CNearFieldOF = 0.0, Total_CFx = 0.0, Total_CFy = 0.0, Total_CFz = 0.0, Total_CMerit = 0.0,
804  Total_CT = 0.0, Total_CQ = 0.0,
805  Total_Heat = 0.0, Total_MaxHeat = 0.0, Total_Temperature = 0.0, Total_Custom_ObjFunc = 0.0,
806  Total_ComboObj = 0.0, Total_NetThrust = 0.0, Total_Power = 0.0, Total_AeroCD = 0.0, Total_SolidCD = 0.0, Total_IDR = 0.0, Total_IDC = 0.0,
807  Total_AoA = 0.0, Total_Buffet_Metric = 0.0;
808  su2double Surface_MassFlow = 0.0, Surface_Mach = 0.0, Surface_Temperature = 0.0, Surface_Pressure = 0.0, Surface_Density = 0.0, Surface_Enthalpy = 0.0, Surface_NormalVelocity = 0.0, Surface_TotalTemperature = 0.0, Surface_TotalPressure = 0.0, Surface_Uniformity = 0.0, Surface_SecondaryStrength = 0.0,Surface_MomentumDistortion = 0.0, Surface_SecondOverUniform = 0.0, Surface_PressureDrop = 0.0;
809 
810  su2double Total_ForceCoeff = 0.0, Total_VMStress = 0.0, Total_IncLoad = 0.0;
811  su2double Total_SensE = 0.0, Total_SensNu = 0.0;
812 
813  unsigned short iSpan;
814 
815  /*--- Initialize variables to store information from all domains (adjoint solution) ---*/
816  su2double Total_Sens_Geo = 0.0, Total_Sens_Mach = 0.0, Total_Sens_AoA = 0.0;
817  su2double Total_Sens_Press = 0.0, Total_Sens_Temp = 0.0;
818 
819  su2double Total_Sens_BPressure = 0.0;
820  su2double Total_Sens_ModVel = 0.0;
821 
822  /*--- Initialize variables to store information from all domains (direct differentiation) ---*/
823  su2double D_Total_CL = 0.0, D_Total_CD = 0.0, D_Total_CSF = 0.0, D_Total_CMx = 0.0, D_Total_CMy = 0.0, D_Total_CMz = 0.0, D_Total_CEff = 0.0, D_Total_CFx = 0.0,
824  D_Total_CFy = 0.0, D_Total_CFz = 0.0, D_Total_NetThrust = 0.0, D_Total_Power = 0.0, D_Total_AeroCD = 0.0, D_Total_SolidCD = 0.0, D_Total_IDR = 0.0, D_Total_IDC = 0.0, D_Total_Custom_ObjFunc = 0.0, D_Total_Heat = 0.0, D_Total_MaxHeat = 0.0,
825  D_TotalPressure_Loss = 0.0, D_FlowAngle_Out = 0.0, D_TotalStaticEfficiency = 0.0,
826  D_TotalTotalEfficiency = 0.0, D_EntropyGen = 0.0,
827  D_Surface_Uniformity = 0.0, D_Surface_SecondaryStrength = 0.0, D_Surface_MomentumDistortion = 0.0, D_Surface_SecondOverUniform = 0.0, D_Surface_PressureDrop = 0.0;
828 
829  /*--- Residual arrays ---*/
830  su2double *residual_flow = nullptr,
831  *residual_turbulent = nullptr,
832  *residual_transition = nullptr;
833  su2double *residual_adjflow = nullptr,
834  *residual_adjturbulent = nullptr,
835  *residual_adjheat = nullptr;
836  su2double *residual_fea = nullptr;

856  /*--- Initialize number of variables ---*/

858  nVar_Trans = 0, nVar_Heat = 0,
859  nVar_AdjFlow = 0, nVar_AdjTurb = 0, nVar_AdjHeat = 0,
860  nVar_FEM = 0, nVar_Rad = 0;
861 
862  /*--- Direct problem variables ---*/
863  if (compressible) nVar_Flow = nDim+2; else nVar_Flow = nDim+2;
864  if (turbulent) {
865  switch (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Turb_Model()) {
866  case TURB_MODEL::SA: nVar_Turb = 1; break;
867  case TURB_MODEL::SST: nVar_Turb = 2; break;
868  default: break;
869  }

871  if (transition) nVar_Trans = 2;
872  if (heat) nVar_Heat = 1;
873 
874  if (fem) {

876  if (nonlinear_analysis) nVar_FEM = 3;
877 
878  if (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_FEM) nVar_FEM = nDim;
879 
880  }
881 
882  if (radiation) nVar_Rad = 1;
883 
884  /*--- Adjoint problem variables ---*/
885  if (compressible) nVar_AdjFlow = nDim+2; else nVar_AdjFlow = nDim+2;
886  if (turbulent) {
887  switch (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Turb_Model()) {
888  case TURB_MODEL::SA: nVar_AdjTurb = 1; break;
889  case TURB_MODEL::SST: nVar_AdjTurb = 2; break;
890  default: break;
891  }
892  }
893  if (weakly_coupled_heat) nVar_AdjHeat = 1;
894

896  residual_flow = new su2double[nVar_Flow];
897  residual_turbulent = new su2double[nVar_Turb];
898  residual_transition = new su2double[nVar_Trans];
899  residual_heat = new su2double[nVar_Heat];
900  residual_fem = new su2double[nVar_FEM];
901  residual_rad = new su2double[nVar_Rad];
902  residual_adjflow = new su2double[nVar_AdjFlow];
903  residual_adjturbulent = new su2double[nVar_AdjTurb];
904  residual_adjheat = new su2double[nVar_AdjHeat];
905 
906  /*--- Allocate memory for the coefficients being monitored ---*/
907  aeroelastic_plunge = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
908  aeroelastic_pitch = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
909  Surface_CL = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
910  Surface_CD = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
911  Surface_CSF = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
912  Surface_CEff = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
913  Surface_CFx = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
914  Surface_CFy = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
915  Surface_CFz = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
916  Surface_CMx = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
917  Surface_CMy = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];
918  Surface_CMz = new su2double[config[ZONE_0]->GetnMarker_Monitoring()];

1116  // if (fluid_structure) {

1198  /*--- Linear analysis: RMS of the displacements in the nDim coordinates ---*/
1199  /*--- Nonlinear analysis: UTOL, RTOL and DTOL (defined in the Postprocessing function) ---*/
1200 
1201  if (linear_analysis) {
1202  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_FEM; iVar++) {

1204  }

1209  }
1210  }
1211 
1212  break;
1213 
1214  case MAIN_SOLVER::DISC_ADJ_FEM:
1215 
1216  /*--- FEM coefficients -- As of now, this is the Von Mises Stress ---*/
1217

1219 
1220  /*--- Residuals: ---*/
1221  /*--- Linear analysis: RMS of the displacements in the nDim coordinates ---*/
1222  /*--- Nonlinear analysis: UTOL, RTOL and DTOL (defined in the Postprocessing function) ---*/
1223  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_FEM; iVar++) {
1224  residual_fem[iVar] = solver_container[val_iZone][val_iInst][FinestMesh][ADJFEA_SOL]->GetRes_RMS(iVar);
1225  }

1227  break;

1229  default:
1230  break;
1231 
1232  }

2426 
2427 void COutputLegacy::SpecialOutput_ForcesBreakdown(CSolver *****solver, CGeometry ****geometry, CConfig **config, unsigned short val_iZone, bool output) const {
2428 
2429  char cstr[200];
2430  unsigned short iDim, iMarker_Monitoring;
2431  ofstream Breakdown_file;
2432 
2433  bool compressible = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::COMPRESSIBLE);
2434  bool incompressible = (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::INCOMPRESSIBLE);
2435  bool unsteady = (config[val_iZone]->GetTime_Marching() != TIME_MARCHING::STEADY);
2436  bool viscous = config[val_iZone]->GetViscous();
2437  bool dynamic_grid = config[val_iZone]->GetDynamic_Grid();
2438  bool gravity = config[val_iZone]->GetGravityForce();
2439  bool turbulent = config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::RANS;
2440  bool fixed_cl = config[val_iZone]->GetFixed_CL_Mode();
2441  MAIN_SOLVER Kind_Solver = config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver();
2442  TURB_MODEL Kind_Turb_Model = config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Turb_Model();
2443  unsigned short Ref_NonDim = config[val_iZone]->GetRef_NonDim();
2444 
2445  unsigned short FinestMesh = config[val_iZone]->GetFinestMesh();
2446  unsigned short nDim = geometry[val_iZone][INST_0][FinestMesh]->GetnDim();
2447  bool flow = ((config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::EULER) ||
2448  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::NAVIER_STOKES) ||
2449  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::RANS) ||
2450  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::INC_EULER) ||
2451  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::INC_NAVIER_STOKES) ||
2452  (config[val_iZone]->GetKind_Solver() == MAIN_SOLVER::INC_RANS));
2453 
2454  /*--- Output the mean flow solution using only the master node ---*/
2455 
2456  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (flow) && (output)) {
2457 
2458  cout << endl << "Writing the forces breakdown file ("<< config[val_iZone]->GetBreakdown_FileName() << ")." << endl;
2459 
2460  /*--- Initialize variables to store information from all domains (direct solution) ---*/
2461 
2462  su2double Total_CL = 0.0, Total_CD = 0.0, Total_CSF = 0.0,
2463  Total_CMx = 0.0, Total_CMy = 0.0, Total_CMz = 0.0, Total_CEff = 0.0,
2464  Total_CoPx = 0.0, Total_CoPy = 0.0, Total_CoPz = 0.0,
2465  Total_CFx = 0.0, Total_CFy = 0.0, Total_CFz = 0.0, Inv_CL = 0.0,
2466  Inv_CD = 0.0, Inv_CSF = 0.0, Inv_CMx = 0.0, Inv_CMy = 0.0,
2467  Inv_CMz = 0.0, Inv_CEff = 0.0, Inv_CFx = 0.0, Inv_CFy = 0.0, Inv_CFz =

4281 void COutputLegacy::SpecialOutput_SpanLoad(CSolver *solver, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, bool output) const {
4282 
4283  short iSection, nSection;
4284  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, Trailing_Point;
4285  su2double *Plane_P0, *Plane_P0_, *Plane_Normal, *Plane_Normal_, *CPressure,
4286  Force[3], ForceInviscid[3], MomentInviscid[3] =
4287  { 0.0, 0.0, 0.0 }, MomentDist[3] = { 0.0, 0.0, 0.0 }, RefDensity,
4288  RefPressure, RefArea, *Velocity_Inf, Gas_Constant, Mach2Vel,
4289  Mach_Motion, Gamma, RefVel2 = 0.0, factor, NDPressure,
4290  RefLength, Alpha, CL_Inv,
4291  Xcoord_LeadingEdge = 0.0, Ycoord_LeadingEdge = 0.0, Zcoord_LeadingEdge = 0.0,
4292  Xcoord_TrailingEdge = 0.0, Ycoord_TrailingEdge = 0.0, Zcoord_TrailingEdge = 0.0,
4293  Xcoord_LeadingEdge_ = 0.0,
4294  Xcoord_TrailingEdge_ = 0.0, Ycoord_TrailingEdge_ = 0.0, Zcoord_TrailingEdge_ = 0.0,
4295  MaxDistance, Distance, Chord, Aux, Dihedral_Trailing;
4296 
4297  su2double B, Y, C_L, C_L0, Elliptic_Spanload;
4298 
4299  vector<su2double> Xcoord_Airfoil, Ycoord_Airfoil, Zcoord_Airfoil,
4300  CPressure_Airfoil;
4301  vector<su2double> Xcoord_Airfoil_, Ycoord_Airfoil_, Zcoord_Airfoil_,
4302  CPressure_Airfoil_;
4303  string Marker_Tag, Slice_Filename, Slice_Ext;
4304  ofstream Cp_File;
4305  unsigned short iDim;
4306 
4307  bool dynamic_grid = config->GetDynamic_Grid();
4308 
4309  Plane_P0 = new su2double[3];
4310  Plane_P0_ = new su2double[3];
4311  Plane_Normal = new su2double[3];
4312  Plane_Normal_ = new su2double[3];
4313  CPressure = new su2double[geometry->GetnPoint()];
4314 
4315  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (output)) {
4316  cout << endl << "Writing the spanload file (load_distribution.dat).";
4317  }
4318 
4319  /*--- Compute some reference quantities and necessary values ---*/
4320 
4321  RefDensity = solver->GetDensity_Inf();
4322  RefPressure = solver->GetPressure_Inf();
4323  RefArea = config->GetRefArea();
4324  Velocity_Inf = solver->GetVelocity_Inf();
4325  Gamma = config->GetGamma();
4326  const auto Origin = config->GetRefOriginMoment(0);
4327  RefLength = config->GetRefLength();
4328  Alpha = config->GetAoA() * PI_NUMBER / 180.0;
4329 
4330  if (dynamic_grid) {
4331  Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
4332  Mach2Vel = sqrt(
4333  Gamma * Gas_Constant * config->GetTemperature_FreeStreamND());
4334  Mach_Motion = config->GetMach_Motion();
4335  RefVel2 = (Mach_Motion * Mach2Vel) * (Mach_Motion * Mach2Vel);
4336  } else {
4337  RefVel2 = 0.0;
4338  for (iDim = 0; iDim < geometry->GetnDim(); iDim++)
4339  RefVel2 += Velocity_Inf[iDim] * Velocity_Inf[iDim];
4340  }
4341  factor = 1.0 / (0.5 * RefDensity * RefArea * RefVel2);
4342 
4343  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) {
4344 
4345  /*--- Copy the pressure to an auxiliar structure ---*/
4346 
4347  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < geometry->GetnPoint(); iPoint++) {
4348  CPressure[iPoint] = (solver->GetNodes()->GetPressure(iPoint)
4349  - RefPressure) * factor * RefArea;
4350  }
4351 
4352  nSection = config->GetnLocationStations();
4353 
4354  for (iSection = 0; iSection < nSection; iSection++) {
4355 
4356  /*--- Read the values from the config file ---*/
4357 
4358  Plane_Normal[0] = 0.0; Plane_P0[0] = 0.0;
4359  Plane_Normal[1] = 0.0; Plane_P0[1] = 0.0;
4360  Plane_Normal[2] = 0.0; Plane_P0[2] = 0.0;
4361 
4362  if (config->GetGeo_Description() == FUSELAGE) {
4363  Plane_Normal[0] = 1.0;
4364  Plane_P0[0] = config->GetLocationStations(iSection);
4365  }
4366  else if (config->GetGeo_Description() == NACELLE) {
4367  Plane_Normal[0] = 0.0;
4368  Plane_Normal[1] = -sin(config->GetLocationStations(iSection)*PI_NUMBER/180.0);
4369  Plane_Normal[2] = cos(config->GetLocationStations(iSection)*PI_NUMBER/180.0);
4370 
4371  /*--- Apply tilt angle to the plane ---*/
4372 
4373  su2double Tilt_Angle = config->GetNacelleLocation(3)*PI_NUMBER/180;
4374  su2double Plane_NormalX_Tilt = Plane_Normal[0]*cos(Tilt_Angle) + Plane_Normal[2]*sin(Tilt_Angle);
4375  su2double Plane_NormalY_Tilt = Plane_Normal[1];
4376  su2double Plane_NormalZ_Tilt = Plane_Normal[2]*cos(Tilt_Angle) - Plane_Normal[0]*sin(Tilt_Angle);
4377 
4378  /*--- Apply toe angle to the plane ---*/
4379 
4380  su2double Toe_Angle = config->GetNacelleLocation(4)*PI_NUMBER/180;
4381  su2double Plane_NormalX_Tilt_Toe = Plane_NormalX_Tilt*cos(Toe_Angle) - Plane_NormalY_Tilt*sin(Toe_Angle);
4382  su2double Plane_NormalY_Tilt_Toe = Plane_NormalX_Tilt*sin(Toe_Angle) + Plane_NormalY_Tilt*cos(Toe_Angle);
4383  su2double Plane_NormalZ_Tilt_Toe = Plane_NormalZ_Tilt;
4384 
4385  /*--- Update normal vector ---*/
4386 
4387  Plane_Normal[0] = Plane_NormalX_Tilt_Toe;
4388  Plane_Normal[1] = Plane_NormalY_Tilt_Toe;
4389  Plane_Normal[2] = Plane_NormalZ_Tilt_Toe;
4390 
4391  }
4392  else {
4393  Plane_Normal[1] = 1.0;
4394  Plane_P0[1] = config->GetLocationStations(iSection);
4395  }
4396 
4397  /*--- Compute the airfoil sections (note that we feed in the Cp) ---*/
4398 
4399  geometry->ComputeAirfoil_Section(Plane_P0, Plane_Normal, -1E6, 1E6, -1E6, 1E6, -1E6, 1E6,
4400  CPressure, Xcoord_Airfoil, Ycoord_Airfoil, Zcoord_Airfoil,
4401  CPressure_Airfoil, true, config);
4402 
4403  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (Xcoord_Airfoil.size() == 0)) {
4404  if ((config->GetGeo_Description() == FUSELAGE) || (config->GetGeo_Description() == WING))
4405  cout << endl << "Please check the config file, the section (" << Plane_P0[0] <<", " << Plane_P0[1] <<", " << Plane_P0[2] << ") has not been detected." << endl;
4406  if (config->GetGeo_Description() == NACELLE)
4407  cout << endl << "Please check the config file, the section (" << Plane_Normal[0] <<", " << Plane_Normal[1] <<", " << Plane_Normal[2] << ") has not been detected." << endl;
4408  }
4409 
4410 
4411  /*--- Compute dihedral using a step in the station value ---*/
4412 
4413  Plane_P0_[0] = 0.0; Plane_Normal_[0] = 0.0;
4414  Plane_P0_[1] = 0.0; Plane_Normal_[1] = 0.0;
4415  Plane_P0_[2] = 0.0; Plane_Normal_[2] = 0.0;
4416 
4417  if (config->GetGeo_Description() == FUSELAGE) {
4418  Plane_Normal_[0] = 1.0;
4419  if (iSection == 0) Plane_P0_[0] = config->GetLocationStations(iSection) + 0.01;
4420  else Plane_P0_[0] = config->GetLocationStations(iSection) - 0.01;
4421  }
4422  else if (config->GetGeo_Description() == NACELLE) {
4423  if (iSection == 0) {
4424  Plane_Normal_[0] = 0.0;
4425  Plane_Normal_[1] = -sin((config->GetLocationStations(iSection) + 0.01)*PI_NUMBER/180.0);
4426  Plane_Normal_[2] = cos((config->GetLocationStations(iSection) + 0.01)*PI_NUMBER/180.0);
4427 
4428  /*--- Apply tilt angle to the plane ---*/
4429 
4430  su2double Tilt_Angle = config->GetNacelleLocation(3)*PI_NUMBER/180;
4431  su2double Plane_NormalX_Tilt = Plane_Normal[0]*cos(Tilt_Angle) + Plane_Normal[2]*sin(Tilt_Angle);
4432  su2double Plane_NormalY_Tilt = Plane_Normal[1];
4433  su2double Plane_NormalZ_Tilt = Plane_Normal[2]*cos(Tilt_Angle) - Plane_Normal[0]*sin(Tilt_Angle);
4434 
4435  /*--- Apply toe angle to the plane ---*/
4436 
4437  su2double Toe_Angle = config->GetNacelleLocation(4)*PI_NUMBER/180;
4438  su2double Plane_NormalX_Tilt_Toe = Plane_NormalX_Tilt*cos(Toe_Angle) - Plane_NormalY_Tilt*sin(Toe_Angle);
4439  su2double Plane_NormalY_Tilt_Toe = Plane_NormalX_Tilt*sin(Toe_Angle) + Plane_NormalY_Tilt*cos(Toe_Angle);
4440  su2double Plane_NormalZ_Tilt_Toe = Plane_NormalZ_Tilt;
4441 
4442  /*--- Update normal vector ---*/
4443 
4444  Plane_Normal[0] = Plane_NormalX_Tilt_Toe;
4445  Plane_Normal[1] = Plane_NormalY_Tilt_Toe;
4446  Plane_Normal[2] = Plane_NormalZ_Tilt_Toe;
4447 
4448  }
4449  else {
4450  Plane_Normal_[0] = 0.0;
4451  Plane_Normal_[1] = -sin((config->GetLocationStations(iSection) - 0.01)*PI_NUMBER/180.0);
4452  Plane_Normal_[2] = cos((config->GetLocationStations(iSection) - 0.01)*PI_NUMBER/180.0);
4453 
4454  /*--- Apply tilt angle to the plane ---*/
4455 
4456  su2double Tilt_Angle = config->GetNacelleLocation(3)*PI_NUMBER/180;
4457  su2double Plane_NormalX_Tilt = Plane_Normal[0]*cos(Tilt_Angle) + Plane_Normal[2]*sin(Tilt_Angle);
4458  su2double Plane_NormalY_Tilt = Plane_Normal[1];
4459  su2double Plane_NormalZ_Tilt = Plane_Normal[2]*cos(Tilt_Angle) - Plane_Normal[0]*sin(Tilt_Angle);
4460 
4461  /*--- Apply toe angle to the plane ---*/
4462 
4463  su2double Toe_Angle = config->GetNacelleLocation(4)*PI_NUMBER/180;
4464  su2double Plane_NormalX_Tilt_Toe = Plane_NormalX_Tilt*cos(Toe_Angle) - Plane_NormalY_Tilt*sin(Toe_Angle);
4465  su2double Plane_NormalY_Tilt_Toe = Plane_NormalX_Tilt*sin(Toe_Angle) + Plane_NormalY_Tilt*cos(Toe_Angle);
4466  su2double Plane_NormalZ_Tilt_Toe = Plane_NormalZ_Tilt;
4467 
4468  /*--- Update normal vector ---*/
4469 
4470  Plane_Normal[0] = Plane_NormalX_Tilt_Toe;
4471  Plane_Normal[1] = Plane_NormalY_Tilt_Toe;
4472  Plane_Normal[2] = Plane_NormalZ_Tilt_Toe;
4473 
4474  }
4475  }
4476  else {
4477  Plane_Normal_[1] = 1.0;
4478  if (iSection == 0) Plane_P0_[1] = config->GetLocationStations(iSection) + 0.01;
4479  else Plane_P0_[1] = config->GetLocationStations(iSection) - 0.01;
4480  }
4481 
4482  geometry->ComputeAirfoil_Section(Plane_P0_, Plane_Normal_, -1E6, 1E6, -1E6, 1E6, -1E6, 1E6,
4483  CPressure, Xcoord_Airfoil_, Ycoord_Airfoil_, Zcoord_Airfoil_,
4484  CPressure_Airfoil_, true, config);
4485 
4486  /*--- Output the pressure on each section (tecplot format) ---*/
4487 
4488  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && (Xcoord_Airfoil.size() != 0)) {
4489 
4490  /*--- Find leading and trailing edge ---*/
4491 
4492  Xcoord_LeadingEdge = 1E6; Xcoord_TrailingEdge = -1E6;
4493  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_Airfoil.size(); iVertex++) {
4494  if (Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] < Xcoord_LeadingEdge) {
4495  Xcoord_LeadingEdge = Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex];
4496  Ycoord_LeadingEdge = Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex];
4497  Zcoord_LeadingEdge = Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex];
4498  }
4499  if (Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] > Xcoord_TrailingEdge) {
4500  Xcoord_TrailingEdge = Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex];
4501  Ycoord_TrailingEdge = Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex];
4502  Zcoord_TrailingEdge = Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex];
4503  }
4504  }
4505 
4506  Chord = (Xcoord_TrailingEdge-Xcoord_LeadingEdge);
4507 
4508  /*--- Compute dihedral ---*/
4509 
4510  Xcoord_LeadingEdge_ = 1E6; Xcoord_TrailingEdge_ = -1E6;
4511  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_Airfoil_.size(); iVertex++) {
4512  if (Xcoord_Airfoil_[iVertex] < Xcoord_LeadingEdge_) {
4513  Xcoord_LeadingEdge_ = Xcoord_Airfoil_[iVertex];
4514  }
4515  if (Xcoord_Airfoil_[iVertex] > Xcoord_TrailingEdge_) {
4516  Xcoord_TrailingEdge_ = Xcoord_Airfoil_[iVertex];
4517  Ycoord_TrailingEdge_ = Ycoord_Airfoil_[iVertex];
4518  Zcoord_TrailingEdge_ = Zcoord_Airfoil_[iVertex];
4519  }
4520  }
4521 
4522  if (iSection == 0) {
4523  Dihedral_Trailing = atan((Zcoord_TrailingEdge_ - Zcoord_TrailingEdge) / (Ycoord_TrailingEdge_ - Ycoord_TrailingEdge))*180/PI_NUMBER;
4524  }
4525  else {
4526  Dihedral_Trailing = atan((Zcoord_TrailingEdge - Zcoord_TrailingEdge_) / (Ycoord_TrailingEdge - Ycoord_TrailingEdge_))*180/PI_NUMBER;
4527  }
4528 
4529  /*--- Write Cp at each section (tecplot format) ---*/
4530 
4531  if (output) {
4532 
4533  ofstream Cp_File;
4534 
4535  if (iSection == 0) {
4536  Cp_File.open("cp_sections.dat", ios::out);
4537  Cp_File << "TITLE = \"Airfoil sections\"" << endl;
4538  Cp_File << "VARIABLES = \"x/c\",\"C<sub>p</sub>\",\"x\",\"y\",\"z\",\"y/c\",\"z/c\"" << endl;
4539  } else
4540  Cp_File.open("cp_sections.dat", ios::app);
4541 
4542  if (config->GetGeo_Description() == NACELLE) {
4543  su2double theta_deg = atan2(Plane_Normal[1], -Plane_Normal[2])/PI_NUMBER*180 + 180;
4544  Cp_File << "ZONE T=\"Theta = " << theta_deg << " deg\", I= " << Xcoord_Airfoil.size() << ", F=POINT" << "\n";
4545  }
4546  else {
4547  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) Cp_File << "ZONE T=\"y = " << Plane_P0[1] << " m\", I= "
4548  << Xcoord_Airfoil.size() << ", F=POINT" << "\n";
4549 
4550  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) Cp_File << "ZONE T=\"y = " << Plane_P0[1]*12.0 << " in\", I= "
4551  << Xcoord_Airfoil.size() << ", F=POINT" << "\n";
4552  }
4553 
4554 
4555 
4556  /*--- Coordinates and pressure value ---*/
4557 
4558  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_Airfoil.size(); iVertex++) {
4559 
4560  su2double XCoord = Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex];
4561  su2double YCoord = Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex];
4562  su2double ZCoord = Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex];
4563 
4564  /*--- Undo the transformation based on the Theta angle ---*/
4565 
4566  if (config->GetGeo_Description() == NACELLE) {
4567  su2double theta_deg = atan2(Plane_Normal[1],-Plane_Normal[2])/PI_NUMBER*180 + 180;
4568  su2double Angle = theta_deg*PI_NUMBER/180 - 0.5*PI_NUMBER;
4569 
4570  XCoord = Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] + config->GetNacelleLocation(0);
4571  YCoord = (Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex]*cos(Angle) - Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex]*sin(Angle)) + config->GetNacelleLocation(1);
4572  ZCoord = (Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex]*cos(Angle) + Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex]*sin(Angle)) + config->GetNacelleLocation(2);
4573 
4574  }
4575 
4576  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) {
4577  Cp_File << (Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] - Xcoord_LeadingEdge) / Chord << " " << CPressure_Airfoil[iVertex]
4578  << " " << XCoord * 12.0 << " " << YCoord * 12.0 << " " << ZCoord * 12.0
4579  << " " << (Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex] - Ycoord_LeadingEdge) / Chord << " " << (Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] - Zcoord_LeadingEdge) / Chord << "\n";
4580  }
4581  else {
4582  Cp_File << (Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] - Xcoord_LeadingEdge) / Chord << " " << CPressure_Airfoil[iVertex]
4583  << " " << XCoord << " " << YCoord << " " << ZCoord
4584  << " " << (Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex] - Ycoord_LeadingEdge) / Chord << " " << (Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] - Zcoord_LeadingEdge) / Chord << "\n";
4585  }
4586 
4587  }
4588 
4589  Cp_File.close();
4590 
4591  }
4592 
4593  /*--- Compute load distribution ---*/
4594 
4595  ForceInviscid[0] = 0.0; ForceInviscid[1] = 0.0; ForceInviscid[2] = 0.0; MomentInviscid[1] = 0.0;
4596 
4597  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Xcoord_Airfoil.size() - 1; iVertex++) {
4598 
4599  NDPressure = 0.5 * (CPressure_Airfoil[iVertex] + CPressure_Airfoil[iVertex + 1]);
4600 
4601  Force[0] = -(Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex + 1] - Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex]) * NDPressure;
4602  Force[1] = 0.0;
4603  Force[2] = (Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex + 1] - Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex]) * NDPressure;
4604 
4605  ForceInviscid[0] += Force[0];
4606  ForceInviscid[1] += Force[1];
4607  ForceInviscid[2] += Force[2];
4608 
4609  MomentDist[0] = 0.5 * (Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] + Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex + 1]) - Origin[0];
4610  MomentDist[1] = 0.5 * (Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex] + Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex + 1]) - Origin[1];
4611  MomentDist[2] = 0.5 * (Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] + Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex + 1]) - Origin[3];
4612 
4613  MomentInviscid[1] += (Force[0] * MomentDist[2] - Force[2] * MomentDist[0]) / RefLength;
4614 
4615  }
4616 
4617  /*--- Compute local chord, for the nondimensionalization ---*/
4618 
4619  MaxDistance = 0.0; Trailing_Point = 0;
4620 
4621  for (iVertex = 1; iVertex < Xcoord_Airfoil.size(); iVertex++) {
4622 
4623  Distance = sqrt(pow(Xcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] - Xcoord_Airfoil[Trailing_Point], 2.0) +
4624  pow(Ycoord_Airfoil[iVertex] - Ycoord_Airfoil[Trailing_Point], 2.0) +
4625  pow(Zcoord_Airfoil[iVertex] - Zcoord_Airfoil[Trailing_Point], 2.0));
4626 
4627  if (MaxDistance < Distance) { MaxDistance = Distance; }
4628 
4629  }
4630 
4631  Chord = MaxDistance;
4632 
4633  CL_Inv = cos(Dihedral_Trailing * PI_NUMBER / 180.0) * fabs( -ForceInviscid[0] * sin(Alpha) + ForceInviscid[2] * cos(Alpha) )/ Chord;
4634 
4635  /*--- Compute sectional lift at the root ---*/
4636 
4637  B = 2.0*config->GetSemiSpan();
4638  RefArea = config->GetRefArea();
4639  C_L = solver->GetTotal_CL();
4640  C_L0 = 8.0*C_L*RefArea/(B*PI_NUMBER);
4641  Y = Ycoord_Airfoil[0];
4642  Aux = Y/(0.5*B);
4643  Elliptic_Spanload = (C_L0 / RefLength) * sqrt(fabs(1.0-Aux*Aux));
4644 
4645 
4646  /*--- Write load distribution ---*/
4647 
4648  if (output) {
4649 
4650  ofstream Load_File;
4651  if (iSection == 0) {
4652 
4653  if ((config->GetTabular_FileFormat() == TAB_OUTPUT::TAB_CSV)) {
4654  Load_File.open("load_distribution.csv", ios::out);
4655  Load_File << "\"Percent Semispan\",\"Sectional C_L\",\"Spanload (c C_L / c_ref) \",\"Elliptic Spanload\"" << endl;
4656  }
4657  else {
4658  Load_File.open("load_distribution.dat", ios::out);
4659  Load_File << "TITLE = \"Load distribution\"" << endl;
4660  Load_File << "VARIABLES = \"Percent Semispan\",\"Sectional C<sub>L</sub>\",\"Spanload (c C<sub>L</sub> / c<sub>ref</sub>) \",\"Elliptic Spanload\"" << endl;
4661  Load_File << "ZONE T=\"Wing load distribution\"" << endl;
4662  }
4663  } else {
4664  if ((config->GetTabular_FileFormat() == TAB_OUTPUT::TAB_CSV)) Load_File.open("load_distribution.csv", ios::app);
4665  else Load_File.open("load_distribution.dat", ios::app);
4666  }
4667 
4668 
4669  /*--- CL and spanload ---*/
4670 
4671  if ((config->GetTabular_FileFormat() == TAB_OUTPUT::TAB_CSV))
4672  Load_File << 100.0*Ycoord_Airfoil[0]/(0.5*B) << ", " << CL_Inv << ", " << Chord*CL_Inv / RefLength <<", " << Elliptic_Spanload << endl;
4673  else
4674  Load_File << 100.0*Ycoord_Airfoil[0]/(0.5*B) << " " << CL_Inv << " " << Chord*CL_Inv / RefLength <<" " << Elliptic_Spanload << endl;
4675 
4676  Load_File.close();
4677 
4678  }
4679 
4680  }
4681 
4682  }
4683 
4684  }
4685 
4686  /*--- Delete dynamically allocated memory ---*/
4687 
4688  delete[] Plane_P0;
4689  delete[] Plane_P0_;
4690  delete[] Plane_Normal;
4691  delete[] Plane_Normal_;
4692  delete[] CPressure;
4693 
4694 }

4697 void COutputLegacy::SetCp_InverseDesign(CSolver *solver_container, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, unsigned long iExtIter) {
4698 
4699  unsigned short iMarker, icommas, Boundary, iDim;
4700  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint, (*Point2Vertex)[2], nPointLocal = 0, nPointGlobal = 0;
4701  su2double XCoord, YCoord, ZCoord, Pressure, PressureCoeff = 0, Cp, CpTarget, *Normal = nullptr, Area, PressDiff;
4702  bool *PointInDomain;
4703  string text_line, surfCp_filename;
4704  ifstream Surface_file;
4705  char buffer[50], cstr[200];
4706 
4707 
4708  nPointLocal = geometry->GetnPoint();
4709 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
4710  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&nPointLocal, &nPointGlobal, 1, MPI_UNSIGNED_LONG, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
4711 #else
4712  nPointGlobal = nPointLocal;
4713 #endif
4714 
4715  Point2Vertex = new unsigned long[nPointGlobal][2];
4716  PointInDomain = new bool[nPointGlobal];
4717 
4718  for (iPoint = 0; iPoint < nPointGlobal; iPoint ++)
4719  PointInDomain[iPoint] = false;
4720 
4721  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
4722  Boundary = config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker);
4723 
4724  if ((Boundary == EULER_WALL ) ||
4725  (Boundary == HEAT_FLUX ) ||
4726  (Boundary == ISOTHERMAL ) ||
4727  (Boundary == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)) {
4728  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
4729 
4730  /*--- The Pressure file uses the global numbering ---*/
4731 
4732 #ifndef HAVE_MPI
4733  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
4734 #else
4735  iPoint = geometry->nodes->GetGlobalIndex(geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode());
4736 #endif
4737 
4738  if (geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode() < geometry->GetnPointDomain()) {
4739  Point2Vertex[iPoint][0] = iMarker;
4740  Point2Vertex[iPoint][1] = iVertex;
4741  PointInDomain[iPoint] = true;
4742  solver_container->SetCPressureTarget(iMarker, iVertex, 0.0);
4743  }
4744 
4745  }
4746  }
4747  }
4748 
4749  /*--- Prepare to read the surface pressure files (CSV) ---*/
4750 
4751  surfCp_filename = "TargetCp";
4752  strcpy (cstr, surfCp_filename.c_str());
4753 
4754  /*--- Write file name with extension if unsteady or steady ---*/
4755 
4756  if (((config->GetTime_Marching() != TIME_MARCHING::STEADY) && config->GetTime_Domain()) ||
4757  (config->GetTime_Marching() == TIME_MARCHING::HARMONIC_BALANCE)) {
4758  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 0) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 10)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_0000%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
4759  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 10) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 100)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_000%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
4760  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 100) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 1000)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_00%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
4761  if ((SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 1000) && (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) < 10000)) SPRINTF (buffer, "_0%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
4762  if (SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter) >= 10000) SPRINTF (buffer, "_%d.dat", SU2_TYPE::Int(iExtIter));
4763  }
4764  else
4765  SPRINTF (buffer, ".dat");
4766 
4767  strcat (cstr, buffer);
4768 
4769  /*--- Read the surface pressure file ---*/
4770 
4771  string::size_type position;
4772 
4773  Surface_file.open(cstr, ios::in);
4774 
4775  if (!(Surface_file.fail())) {
4776 
4777  getline(Surface_file, text_line);
4778 
4779  while (getline(Surface_file, text_line)) {
4780  for (icommas = 0; icommas < 50; icommas++) {
4781  position = text_line.find( ",", 0 );
4782  if (position!=string::npos) text_line.erase (position,1);
4783  }
4784  stringstream point_line(text_line);
4785 
4786  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 2) point_line >> iPoint >> XCoord >> YCoord >> Pressure >> PressureCoeff;
4787  if (geometry->GetnDim() == 3) point_line >> iPoint >> XCoord >> YCoord >> ZCoord >> Pressure >> PressureCoeff;
4788 
4789  if (PointInDomain[iPoint]) {
4790 
4791  /*--- Find the vertex for the Point and Marker ---*/
4792 
4793  iMarker = Point2Vertex[iPoint][0];
4794  iVertex = Point2Vertex[iPoint][1];
4795 
4796  solver_container->SetCPressureTarget(iMarker, iVertex, PressureCoeff);
4797 
4798  }
4799 
4800  }
4801 
4802  Surface_file.close();
4803 
4804  }
4805 
4806  /*--- Compute the pressure difference ---*/
4807 
4808  PressDiff = 0.0;
4809  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
4810  Boundary = config->GetMarker_All_KindBC(iMarker);
4811 
4812  if ((Boundary == EULER_WALL ) ||
4813  (Boundary == HEAT_FLUX ) ||
4814  (Boundary == ISOTHERMAL ) ||
4815  (Boundary == NEARFIELD_BOUNDARY)) {
4816  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
4817 
4818  Normal = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
4819 
4820  Cp = solver_container->GetCPressure(iMarker, iVertex);
4821  CpTarget = solver_container->GetCPressureTarget(iMarker, iVertex);
4822 
4823  Area = 0.0;
4824  for (iDim = 0; iDim < geometry->GetnDim(); iDim++)
4825  Area += Normal[iDim]*Normal[iDim];
4826  Area = sqrt(Area);
4827 
4828  PressDiff += Area * (CpTarget - Cp) * (CpTarget - Cp);
4829  }
4830 
4831  }
4832  }
4833 
4834 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
4835  su2double MyPressDiff = PressDiff; PressDiff = 0.0;
4836  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(&MyPressDiff, &PressDiff, 1, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
4837 #endif
4838 
4839  /*--- Update the total Cp difference coeffient ---*/
4840 
4841  solver_container->SetTotal_CpDiff(PressDiff);
4842 
4843  delete [] Point2Vertex;
4844  delete [] PointInDomain;
4845 
4846 }

5001 void COutputLegacy::SpecialOutput_Distortion(CSolver *solver, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, bool output) const {
5002 
5003  unsigned short iMarker, iDim, iMarker_Analyze;
5004  unsigned long iPoint, iVertex;

5164  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {

5166  if (Marker_TagBound == Analyze_TagBound) {
5167 
5168  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->GetnVertex(iMarker); iVertex++) {
5169  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
5170 
5171  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
5172 
5173  Buffer_Send_Coord_x[nVertex_Surface] = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 0);
5174  Buffer_Send_Coord_y[nVertex_Surface] = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 1);
5175  if (nDim == 3) { Buffer_Send_Coord_z[nVertex_Surface] = geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 2); }
5176 
5177  Pressure = solver->GetNodes()->GetPressure(iPoint);
5178  Density = solver->GetNodes()->GetDensity(iPoint);
5179  Temperature = solver->GetNodes()->GetTemperature(iPoint);
5180  SoundSpeed = solver->GetNodes()->GetSoundSpeed(iPoint);
5181  Velocity2 = solver->GetNodes()->GetVelocity2(iPoint);
5182  Mach = sqrt(Velocity2)/SoundSpeed;
5183  Gamma = config->GetGamma();
5184 
5185  Mach_Inf = config->GetMach();
5186  Pressure_Inf = config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND();
5187  Temperature_Inf = config->GetTemperature_FreeStreamND();
5188  Velocity_Inf = sqrt(config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[0]*config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[0]
5189  + config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[1]*config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[1]
5190  + config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[2]*config->GetVelocity_FreeStreamND()[2]);
5191 
5192  Buffer_Send_P[nVertex_Surface] = Pressure / Pressure_Inf;
5193  Buffer_Send_T[nVertex_Surface] = Temperature / Temperature_Inf;
5194  Buffer_Send_Mach[nVertex_Surface] = Mach;
5195 
5196  TotalPressure = Pressure * pow( 1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
5197  TotalPressure_Inf = Pressure_Inf * pow( 1.0 + Mach_Inf * Mach_Inf * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
5198  Buffer_Send_PT[nVertex_Surface] = TotalPressure / TotalPressure_Inf;
5199 
5200  TotalTemperature = Temperature * (1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0));
5201  TotalTemperature_Inf = Temperature_Inf * (1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0));
5202  Buffer_Send_TT[nVertex_Surface] = TotalTemperature / TotalTemperature_Inf;
5203 
5204  Buffer_Send_Vel_x[nVertex_Surface] = solver->GetNodes()->GetVelocity(iPoint,0) / Velocity_Inf;
5205  Buffer_Send_Vel_y[nVertex_Surface] = solver->GetNodes()->GetVelocity(iPoint,1) / Velocity_Inf;
5206  if (nDim == 3) {
5207  Buffer_Send_Vel_z[nVertex_Surface] = solver->GetNodes()->GetVelocity(iPoint,2) / Velocity_Inf;
5208  }
5209 
5210  Buffer_Send_q[nVertex_Surface] = 0.5*Density*Velocity2;
5211 
5212  Vector = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal();
5213  Area = 0.0; for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) { Area += Vector[iDim]*Vector[iDim]; } Area = sqrt(Area);
5214  Buffer_Send_Area[nVertex_Surface] = Area;
5215 
5216  /*--- If US system, the output should be in inches ---*/
5217 
5218  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) {
5219 
5220  Buffer_Send_Coord_x[nVertex_Surface] *= 12.0;
5221  Buffer_Send_Coord_y[nVertex_Surface] *= 12.0;
5222  if (nDim == 3) Buffer_Send_Coord_z[nVertex_Surface] *= 12.0;
5223  Buffer_Send_Area[nVertex_Surface] *= 144.0;
5224 
5225  }
5226 
5227  nVertex_Surface++;
5228 
5229  }
5230  }
5231  break;
5232  }
5233  }

5240  SU2_MPI::Gather(Buffer_Send_Coord_y, MaxLocalVertex_Surface, MPI_DOUBLE, Buffer_Recv_Coord_y, MaxLocalVertex_Surface, MPI_DOUBLE, MASTER_NODE, SU2_MPI::GetComm());

5252 
5253 #else
5254 
5255  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < MaxLocalVertex_Surface; iVertex++) {

5257  Buffer_Recv_Coord_y[iVertex] = Buffer_Send_Coord_y[iVertex];

5259  Buffer_Recv_PT[iVertex] = Buffer_Send_PT[iVertex];
5260  Buffer_Recv_TT[iVertex] = Buffer_Send_TT[iVertex];

5272 
5273  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
5274 
5275  /*--- Compute the location of the critical points of the distortion measure, and center of gravity ---*/
5276 
5277  TotalArea = 0.0; xCoord_CG = 0.0; yCoord_CG = 0.0; zCoord_CG = 0.0; PT_Mean = 0.0; Mach_Mean = 0.0; q_Mean = 0.0;
5278 
5279  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < nProcessor; iProcessor++) {
5280  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Buffer_Recv_nVertex[iProcessor]; iVertex++) {
5281 
5282  /*--- Current index position and global index ---*/
5283 
5284  Total_Index = iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_Surface+iVertex;
5285 
5286  /*--- Retrieve the merged data for this node ---*/
5287 
5288  xCoord = Buffer_Recv_Coord_x[Total_Index];
5289  yCoord = Buffer_Recv_Coord_y[Total_Index];
5290  if (nDim == 3) zCoord = Buffer_Recv_Coord_z[Total_Index];
5291  PT = Buffer_Recv_PT[Total_Index];
5292  Mach = Buffer_Recv_Mach[Total_Index];
5293  q = Buffer_Recv_q[Total_Index];
5294 
5295  Area = Buffer_Recv_Area[Total_Index];
5296  TotalArea += Area;
5297  xCoord_CG += xCoord*Area;
5298  yCoord_CG += yCoord*Area;
5299  zCoord_CG += zCoord*Area;
5300  PT_Mean += PT*Area;
5301  Mach_Mean += PT*Area;
5302  q_Mean += q*Area;
5303 
5304  }
5305  }
5306 
5307  /*--- Evaluate the area averaged pressure and CG ---*/
5308 
5309  xCoord_CG = xCoord_CG / TotalArea;
5310  yCoord_CG = yCoord_CG / TotalArea;
5311  zCoord_CG = zCoord_CG / TotalArea;
5312  PT_Mean /= TotalArea;
5313  Mach_Mean /= TotalArea;
5314  q_Mean /= TotalArea;
5315 
5316  /*--- If it is a half model, CGy = 0 ---*/
5317 
5318  if (Engine_HalfModel) { yCoord_CG = 0.0; }
5319 
5320  /*--- Compute hub and tip radius ---*/
5321 
5322  TipRadius = 1E-6; HubRadius = 1E6;
5323  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < nProcessor; iProcessor++) {
5324  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Buffer_Recv_nVertex[iProcessor]; iVertex++) {
5325 
5326  /*--- Current index position and global index ---*/
5327 
5328  Total_Index = iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_Surface+iVertex;
5329 
5330  /*--- Retrieve the merged data for this node ---*/
5331 
5332  xCoord = Buffer_Recv_Coord_x[Total_Index];
5333  yCoord = Buffer_Recv_Coord_y[Total_Index];
5334  if (nDim == 3) zCoord = Buffer_Recv_Coord_z[Total_Index];
5335 
5336  if (nDim == 2)
5337  Distance = sqrt((xCoord_CG-xCoord)*(xCoord_CG-xCoord) +
5338  (yCoord_CG-yCoord)*(yCoord_CG-yCoord));
5339 
5340  if (nDim == 3)
5341  Distance = sqrt((xCoord_CG-xCoord)*(xCoord_CG-xCoord) +
5342  (yCoord_CG-yCoord)*(yCoord_CG-yCoord) +
5343  (zCoord_CG-zCoord)*(zCoord_CG-zCoord));
5344 
5345  if (Distance > TipRadius) TipRadius = Distance;
5346  if (Distance < HubRadius) HubRadius = Distance;
5347 
5348  }
5349  }
5350 
5351  if (HubRadius/TipRadius < 0.05) HubRadius = 0.0;
5352 
5353  /*--- Evaluate the DC60 parameter ---*/
5354 
5355  Theta = Theta_DC60;
5356  nStation = nStation_DC60;
5357 
5358  nAngle = SU2_TYPE::Int(360/float(Theta));
5359  r = new su2double [nStation+1];
5360 
5361  /*--- Allocate memory ---*/
5362 
5363  PT_Sector = new su2double [nAngle];
5364  ProbeArray = new su2double ** [nAngle];
5365  for (iAngle = 0; iAngle < nAngle; iAngle++) {
5366  ProbeArray[iAngle] = new su2double * [nStation];
5367  for (iStation = 0; iStation < nStation; iStation++) {
5368  ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation] = new su2double [5];
5369  }
5370  }
5371 
5372  /*--- Define the radius for each probe ---*/
5373 
5374  r[0] = HubRadius; r[nStation] = TipRadius;
5375  for (iStation = 1; iStation < nStation; iStation++) {
5376  r[iStation] = sqrt( r[iStation-1]*r[iStation-1] + (r[nStation]*r[nStation] - r[0]*r[0])/float(nStation) );
5377  }
5378 
5379  /*--- Define the probe rack ---*/
5380 
5381  UpVector[0] = 0.0; UpVector[1] = 0.0; UpVector[2] = 1.0;
5382 
5383  for (iAngle = 0; iAngle < nAngle; iAngle++) {
5384 
5385  radians = -iAngle*Theta*2.0*PI_NUMBER/360;
5386  RotatedVector[0] = UpVector[0];
5387  RotatedVector[1] = UpVector[1] * cos(radians) - UpVector[2] * sin(radians);
5388  RotatedVector[2] = UpVector[1] * sin(radians) + UpVector[2] * cos(radians);
5389 
5390  for (iStation = 1; iStation <= nStation; iStation++) {
5391  ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation-1][0] = xCoord_CG+RotatedVector[0]*sqrt(0.5*(r[iStation]*r[iStation]+r[iStation-1]*r[iStation-1]));
5392  ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation-1][1] = yCoord_CG+RotatedVector[1]*sqrt(0.5*(r[iStation]*r[iStation]+r[iStation-1]*r[iStation-1]));
5393  ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation-1][2] = zCoord_CG+RotatedVector[2]*sqrt(0.5*(r[iStation]*r[iStation]+r[iStation-1]*r[iStation-1]));
5394  }
5395 
5396  }
5397 
5398  /*--- Compute the Total pressure at each probe, closes grid point to the location ---*/
5399 
5400  for (iAngle = 0; iAngle < nAngle; iAngle++) {
5401 
5402  for (iStation = 0; iStation < nStation; iStation++) {
5403  xCoord_ = ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][0];
5404  yCoord_ = ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][1];
5405  zCoord_ = ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][2];
5406 
5407  MinDistance = 1E6;
5408 
5409  for (iProcessor = 0; iProcessor < nProcessor; iProcessor++) {
5410  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < Buffer_Recv_nVertex[iProcessor]; iVertex++) {
5411 
5412  Total_Index = iProcessor*MaxLocalVertex_Surface+iVertex;
5413  xCoord = Buffer_Recv_Coord_x[Total_Index];
5414  yCoord = Buffer_Recv_Coord_y[Total_Index];
5415  if (nDim == 3) zCoord = Buffer_Recv_Coord_z[Total_Index];
5416 
5417  dx = (xCoord_ - xCoord); dy = (yCoord_ - yCoord);
5418  if (nDim == 3) dz = (zCoord_ - zCoord);
5419 
5420  Distance = dx*dx + dy*dy; if (nDim == 3) Distance += dz*dz; Distance = sqrt(Distance);
5421 
5422  if (Engine_HalfModel) {
5423 
5424  yCoord = -yCoord;
5425 
5426  dx_ = (xCoord_ - xCoord); dy_ = (yCoord_ - yCoord);
5427  if (nDim == 3) dz_ = (zCoord_ - zCoord);
5428 
5429  Distance_Mirror = dx_*dx_ + dy_*dy_;
5430  if (nDim == 3) Distance_Mirror += dz_*dz_;
5431  Distance_Mirror = sqrt(Distance_Mirror);
5432 
5433  if (Distance_Mirror < Distance) {
5434  Distance = Distance_Mirror;
5435  dx = dx_; dy = dy_;
5436  if (nDim == 3) dz = dz_;
5437  }
5438 
5439  }
5440 
5441  if (Distance <= MinDistance) {
5442  MinDistance = Distance;
5443  ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][3] = Buffer_Recv_PT[Total_Index];
5444  ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][4] = Buffer_Recv_q[Total_Index];
5445  }
5446 
5447  }
5448  }
5449 
5450  }
5451 
5452  }
5453 
5454  /*--- Evaluate the average pressure at each sector, fan face and dynamic pressure ---*/

5456  PT_Mean = 0.0; q_Mean = 0.0;
5457  for (iAngle = 0; iAngle < nAngle; iAngle++) {
5458  PT_Sector[iAngle] = 0.0;
5459  for (iStation = 0; iStation < nStation; iStation++) {
5460  PT_Sector[iAngle] += ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][3]/float(nStation);
5461  PT_Mean += ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][3]/float(nStation*nAngle);
5462  q_Mean += ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][4]/float(nStation*nAngle);
5463  }
5464  }

5467 
5468  PT_Sector_Min = PT_Sector[0];
5469  for (iAngle = 1; iAngle < nAngle; iAngle++) {
5470  if (PT_Sector[iAngle] <= PT_Sector_Min) PT_Sector_Min = PT_Sector[iAngle];
5471  }
5472

5474 
5475  Mach_Inf = config->GetMach();
5476  Gamma = config->GetGamma();
5477  TotalPressure_Inf = config->GetPressure_FreeStreamND() * pow( 1.0 + Mach_Inf * Mach_Inf *
5478  0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
5479 
5480  if (q_Mean != 0.0) DC60 = ((PT_Mean - PT_Sector_Min)*TotalPressure_Inf)/q_Mean;
5481  else DC60 = 0.0;
5482

5496  }

5515  }

5523  }

5529  for (iAngle = 0; iAngle < nAngle; iAngle++) {
5530

5532  RotatedVector[0] = UpVector[0];
5533  RotatedVector[1] = UpVector[1] * cos(radians) - UpVector[2] * sin(radians);
5534  RotatedVector[2] = UpVector[1] * sin(radians) + UpVector[2] * cos(radians);
5535

5537  ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation-1][0] = xCoord_CG+RotatedVector[0]*sqrt(0.5*(r[iStation]*r[iStation]+r[iStation-1]*r[iStation-1]));
5538  ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation-1][1] = yCoord_CG+RotatedVector[1]*sqrt(0.5*(r[iStation]*r[iStation]+r[iStation-1]*r[iStation-1]));
5539  ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation-1][2] = zCoord_CG+RotatedVector[2]*sqrt(0.5*(r[iStation]*r[iStation]+r[iStation-1]*r[iStation-1]));
5540  }
5541 
5542  }

5549  yCoord_ = ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][1];
5550  zCoord_ = ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][2];
5551
