5958  Beta = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][9]/ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5959 
5960  Mach_ij = ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][7];
5961  if (iAngle+1 != nAngle) Mach_ip1j = ProbeArray[iAngle+1][iStation][7];
5962  else Mach_ip1j = ProbeArray[0][iStation][7];
5963  if (iAngle-1 != -1) Mach_im1j = ProbeArray[iAngle-1][iStation][7];
5964  else Mach_im1j = ProbeArray[nAngle-1][iStation][7];
5965  if (iStation+1 != nStation) Mach_ijp1 = ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation+1][7];
5966  else Mach_ijp1 = ProbeArray[iAngle][0][7];
5967  if (iStation-1 != -1) Mach_ijm1 = ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation-1][7];
5968  else Mach_ijm1 = ProbeArray[iAngle][nStation-1][7];
5969  Filtered_Mach = (4.0*Mach_ij+Mach_ip1j+Mach_im1j+Mach_ijp1+Mach_ijm1)/8.0;
5970 
5971  Alpha_ij = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][10]/ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5972  if (iAngle+1 != nAngle) Alpha_ip1j = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle+1][iStation][10]/ProbeArray[iAngle+1][iStation][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5973  else Alpha_ip1j = atan(ProbeArray[0][iStation][10]/ProbeArray[0][iStation][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5974  if (iAngle-1 != -1) Alpha_im1j = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle-1][iStation][10]/ProbeArray[iAngle-1][iStation][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5975  else Alpha_im1j = atan(ProbeArray[nAngle-1][iStation][10]/ProbeArray[nAngle-1][iStation][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5976  if (iStation+1 != nStation) Alpha_ijp1 = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation+1][10]/ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation+1][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5977  else Alpha_ijp1 = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle][0][10]/ProbeArray[iAngle][0][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5978  if (iStation-1 != -1) Alpha_ijm1 = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation-1][10]/ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation-1][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5979  else Alpha_ijm1 = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle][nStation-1][10]/ProbeArray[iAngle][nStation-1][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5980  Filtered_Alpha = (4.0*Alpha_ij+Alpha_ip1j+Alpha_im1j+Alpha_ijp1+Alpha_ijm1)/8.0;
5981 
5982  Beta_ij = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][9]/ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5983  if (iAngle+1 != nAngle) Beta_ip1j = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle+1][iStation][9]/ProbeArray[iAngle+1][iStation][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5984  else Beta_ip1j = atan(ProbeArray[0][iStation][9]/ProbeArray[0][iStation][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5985  if (iAngle-1 != -1) Beta_im1j = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle-1][iStation][9]/ProbeArray[iAngle-1][iStation][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5986  else Beta_im1j = atan(ProbeArray[nAngle-1][iStation][9]/ProbeArray[nAngle-1][iStation][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5987  if (iStation+1 != nStation) Beta_ijp1 = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation+1][9]/ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation+1][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5988  else Beta_ijp1 = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle][0][9]/ProbeArray[iAngle][0][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5989  if (iStation-1 != -1) Beta_ijm1 = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation-1][9]/ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation-1][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5990  else Beta_ijm1 = atan(ProbeArray[iAngle][nStation-1][9]/ProbeArray[iAngle][nStation-1][8])*360.0/(2.0*PI_NUMBER);
5991  Filtered_Beta = (4.0*Beta_ij+Beta_ip1j+Beta_im1j+Beta_ijp1+Beta_ijm1)/8.0;
5992 
5993 
5994  SurfFlow_file
5995  << " " << ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][1]-yCoord_CG
5996  <<" " << ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][2]-zCoord_CG
5997  <<" " << ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][3] <<" " << ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][4]
5998  <<" " << ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][5] <<" " << ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][6]
5999  <<" " << ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][8] <<" " << ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][9]
6000  <<" " << ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][10]
6001  <<" " << Alpha <<" " << Beta << " " << ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation][7]
6002  <<" " << Filtered_Alpha <<" " << Filtered_Beta << " " << Filtered_Mach << endl;
6003 
6004  }
6005  }
6006 
6007  for (iAngle = 0; iAngle < nAngle; iAngle++) {
6008  for (iStation = 0; iStation < nStation-1; iStation++) {
6009  a = iAngle*nStation+iStation; b = a + nStation; c = b+1; d = a +1;
6010  if (iAngle == nAngle-1) { b = iStation; c = b+1; }
6011  SurfFlow_file << a+1 <<" "<< b+1 <<" "<< c+1 <<" "<< d+1 << endl;
6012  }
6013  }
6014 
6015  /*--- Add extra info ---*/
6016 
6017  SurfFlow_file << "TEXT X=14, Y=86, F=HELV-BOLD, C=BLUE, H=2.0, ";
6018  unsigned short RackProbes = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetDistortionRack()[0]);
6019  unsigned short RackAngle = SU2_TYPE::Int(config->GetDistortionRack()[1]);
6020  SurfFlow_file << "T=\"Rack Size: " << RackProbes << " probes at "<< RackAngle << "deg." << "\\" << "\\n";
6021  SurfFlow_file << "Mach " << config->GetMach() << ", Reynolds " << config->GetReynolds() << ", <greek>a</greek> "
6022  << config->GetAoA() << "deg, <greek>b</greek> " << config->GetAoS() << "deg." << "\\" << "\\n";
6023  SurfFlow_file.precision(1);
6024  SurfFlow_file << fixed << "Net Thrust " << solver->GetTotal_NetThrust() << "lbs, Power " << solver->GetTotal_Power() << "HP";
6025  SurfFlow_file.precision(4);
6026  SurfFlow_file << ", MassFlow " << config->GetSurface_MassFlow(iMarker_Analyze) << ",\\" << "\\n";
6027  SurfFlow_file << "IDC " << config->GetSurface_IDC(iMarker_Analyze)*100 << "%, IDCM " << config->GetSurface_IDC_Mach(iMarker_Analyze)*100 << "%, IDR " << config->GetSurface_IDR(iMarker_Analyze)*100 << "%,\\" << "\\n";
6028  SurfFlow_file << "DC60 " << config->GetSurface_DC60(iMarker_Analyze) << ".\"" << endl;
6029 
6030  }
6031 
6032  }
6033 
6034  /*--- Release the recv buffers on the master node ---*/
6035 
6036  delete [] Buffer_Recv_Coord_x;
6037  delete [] Buffer_Recv_Coord_y;
6038  if (nDim == 3) delete [] Buffer_Recv_Coord_z;
6039 
6040  delete [] Buffer_Recv_PT;
6041  delete [] Buffer_Recv_TT;
6042  delete [] Buffer_Recv_P;
6043  delete [] Buffer_Recv_T;
6044  delete [] Buffer_Recv_Mach;
6045  delete [] Buffer_Recv_Vel_x;
6046  delete [] Buffer_Recv_Vel_y;
6047  if (nDim == 3) delete [] Buffer_Recv_Vel_z;
6048  delete [] Buffer_Recv_q;
6049 
6050  delete [] Buffer_Recv_Area;
6051 
6052  delete [] Buffer_Recv_nVertex;
6053 
6054  delete[] r;
6055  for (iAngle = 0; iAngle < nAngle; iAngle++) {
6056  for (iStation = 0; iStation < nStation; iStation++) {
6057  delete[] ProbeArray[iAngle][iStation];
6058  }
6059  }
6060  delete[] ProbeArray;
6061 
6062  }
6063 
6064 // if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && !config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint()) {
6065 //
6066 // cout << "Surface ("<< Analyze_TagBound << "): ";
6067 // cout.precision(4);
6068 // cout.setf(ios::fixed, ios::floatfield);
6069 // cout << setprecision(1) << "IDC " << 100*config->GetSurface_IDC(iMarker_Analyze)
6070 // << "%. IDC Mach " << 100*config->GetSurface_IDC_Mach(iMarker_Analyze)
6071 // << "%. IDR " << 100*config->GetSurface_IDR(iMarker_Analyze)
6072 // << "%. DC60 " << config->GetSurface_DC60(iMarker_Analyze) << "." << endl;
6073 //
6074 // }
6075 
6076  /*--- Release the memory for the remaining buffers and exit ---*/
6077 
6078  delete [] Buffer_Send_Coord_x;
6079  delete [] Buffer_Send_Coord_y;
6080  if (nDim == 3) delete [] Buffer_Send_Coord_z;
6081 
6082  delete [] Buffer_Send_PT;
6083  delete [] Buffer_Send_TT;
6084  delete [] Buffer_Send_P;
6085  delete [] Buffer_Send_T;
6086  delete [] Buffer_Send_Mach;
6087  delete [] Buffer_Send_Vel_x;
6088  delete [] Buffer_Send_Vel_y;
6089  if (nDim == 3) delete [] Buffer_Send_Vel_z;
6090  delete [] Buffer_Send_q;
6091 
6092  delete [] Buffer_Send_Area;
6093 
6094  }
6095 
6096  /*--- Close the tecplot file ---*/
6097 
6098  if (output) {
6099  SurfFlow_file.close();
6100  }
6101 
6102 }

6610 
6611  /*--- MPI Send/Recv buffers ---*/
6612  su2double *sbuf_var = nullptr, *rbuf_var = nullptr;
6613 
6614  /*--- Other variables ---*/
6615  unsigned short iVar, kInst;
6616  unsigned short nVar_output = 5;
6617  unsigned long current_iter = config[ZONE_0]->GetInnerIter();
6618 
6619  /*--- Allocate memory for send buffer ---*/
6620  sbuf_var = new su2double[nVar_output];
6621 
6622  su2double *averages = new su2double[nVar_output];
6623  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_output; iVar++)
6624  averages[iVar] = 0;
6625 
6626  /*--- Allocate memory for receive buffer ---*/
6627  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
6628  rbuf_var = new su2double[nVar_output];
6629 
6630  HB_output_file.precision(15);
6631  HB_output_file.open("HB_output.csv", ios::out);
6632  HB_output_file << "\"time_instance\",\"CL\",\"CD\",\"CMx\",\"CMy\",\"CMz\"" << endl;
6633 
6634  mean_HB_file.precision(15);
6635  if (current_iter == 0 && iInst == 1) {
6636  mean_HB_file.open("history_HB.plt", ios::trunc);
6637  mean_HB_file << "TITLE = \"SU2 HARMONIC BALANCE SIMULATION\"" << endl;
6638  mean_HB_file << "VARIABLES = \"Iteration\",\"CL\",\"CD\",\"CMx\",\"CMy\",\"CMz\",\"CT\",\"CQ\",\"CMerit\"" << endl;
6639  mean_HB_file << "ZONE T= \"Average Convergence History\"" << endl;
6640  }
6641  else
6642  mean_HB_file.open("history_HB.plt", ios::out | ios::app);
6643  }
6644 
6645  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
6646 
6647  /*--- Run through the zones, collecting the output variables
6648  N.B. Summing across processors within a given zone is being done
6649  elsewhere. ---*/
6650  for (kInst = 0; kInst < val_nInst; kInst++) {
6651 
6652  /*--- Flow solution coefficients (parallel) ---*/
6653  sbuf_var[0] = solver[ZONE_0][kInst][MESH_0][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CL();
6654  sbuf_var[1] = solver[ZONE_0][kInst][INST_0][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CD();
6655  sbuf_var[2] = solver[ZONE_0][kInst][INST_0][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CMx();
6656  sbuf_var[3] = solver[ZONE_0][kInst][INST_0][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CMy();
6657  sbuf_var[4] = solver[ZONE_0][kInst][INST_0][FLOW_SOL]->GetTotal_CMz();
6658 
6659  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_output; iVar++) {
6660  rbuf_var[iVar] = sbuf_var[iVar];
6661  }
6662 
6663  HB_output_file << kInst << ", ";
6664  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_output; iVar++)
6665  HB_output_file << rbuf_var[iVar] << ", ";
6666  HB_output_file << endl;
6667 
6668  /*--- Increment the total contributions from each zone, dividing by nZone as you go ---*/
6669  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_output; iVar++) {
6670  averages[iVar] += (1.0/su2double(val_nInst))*rbuf_var[iVar];
6671  }
6672  }
6673  }
6674 
6675  if (rank == MASTER_NODE && iInst == INST_0) {
6676 
6677  mean_HB_file << current_iter << ", ";
6678  for (iVar = 0; iVar < nVar_output; iVar++) {
6679  mean_HB_file << averages[iVar];
6680  if (iVar < nVar_output-1)
6681  mean_HB_file << ", ";
6682  }
6683  mean_HB_file << endl;
6684  }
6685 
6686  if (rank == MASTER_NODE) {
6687  HB_output_file.close();
6688  mean_HB_file.close();
6689  delete [] rbuf_var;
6690  }
6691 
6692  delete [] sbuf_var;
6693  delete [] averages;
6694 }

6696 void COutputLegacy::SetSpecial_Output(CSolver *****solver_container,

6698  CConfig **config,

6701

6705  for (iZone = 0; iZone < val_nZone; iZone++){

6708

6710  if (config[iZone]->GetWrt_ForcesBreakdown())

6712 
6713  }

6716 
6717 void COutputLegacy::SpecialOutput_AnalyzeSurface(CSolver *solver, CGeometry *geometry, CConfig *config, bool output) const {
6718 
6719  unsigned short iDim, iMarker, iMarker_Analyze;
6720  unsigned long iVertex, iPoint;
6721  su2double Mach = 0.0, Pressure, Temperature = 0.0, TotalPressure = 0.0, TotalTemperature = 0.0,
6722  Enthalpy, Velocity[3]= {0.0}, TangVel[3], Velocity2, MassFlow, Density, Area,
6723  AxiFactor = 1.0, SoundSpeed, Vn, Vn2, Vtang2, Weight = 1.0;
6724 
6725  su2double Gas_Constant = config->GetGas_ConstantND();
6726  su2double Gamma = config->GetGamma();
6727  unsigned short nMarker = config->GetnMarker_All();
6728  unsigned short nDim = geometry->GetnDim();
6729  unsigned short Kind_Average = config->GetKind_Average();
6730 
6731  bool compressible = config->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::COMPRESSIBLE;
6732  bool incompressible = config->GetKind_Regime() == ENUM_REGIME::INCOMPRESSIBLE;
6733  bool energy = config->GetEnergy_Equation();
6734 
6735 
6736  bool axisymmetric = config->GetAxisymmetric();
6737  unsigned short nMarker_Analyze = config->GetnMarker_Analyze();
6738 
6739  su2double *Vector = new su2double[nDim];
6740  su2double *Surface_MassFlow = new su2double[nMarker];
6741  su2double *Surface_Mach = new su2double[nMarker];
6742  su2double *Surface_Temperature = new su2double[nMarker];
6743  su2double *Surface_Density = new su2double[nMarker];
6744  su2double *Surface_Enthalpy = new su2double[nMarker];
6745  su2double *Surface_NormalVelocity = new su2double[nMarker];
6746  su2double *Surface_StreamVelocity2 = new su2double[nMarker];
6747  su2double *Surface_TransvVelocity2 = new su2double[nMarker];
6748  su2double *Surface_Pressure = new su2double[nMarker];
6749  su2double *Surface_TotalTemperature = new su2double[nMarker];
6750  su2double *Surface_TotalPressure = new su2double[nMarker];
6751  su2double *Surface_VelocityIdeal = new su2double[nMarker];
6752  su2double *Surface_Area = new su2double[nMarker];
6753  su2double *Surface_MassFlow_Abs = new su2double[nMarker];
6754 
6755  /*--- Compute the numerical fan face Mach number, and the total area of the inflow ---*/
6756 
6757  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < nMarker; iMarker++) {
6758 
6759  Surface_MassFlow[iMarker] = 0.0;
6760  Surface_Mach[iMarker] = 0.0;
6761  Surface_Temperature[iMarker] = 0.0;
6762  Surface_Density[iMarker] = 0.0;
6763  Surface_Enthalpy[iMarker] = 0.0;
6764  Surface_NormalVelocity[iMarker] = 0.0;
6765  Surface_StreamVelocity2[iMarker] = 0.0;
6766  Surface_TransvVelocity2[iMarker] = 0.0;
6767  Surface_Pressure[iMarker] = 0.0;
6768  Surface_TotalTemperature[iMarker] = 0.0;
6769  Surface_TotalPressure[iMarker] = 0.0;
6770  Surface_VelocityIdeal[iMarker] = 0.0;
6771  Surface_Area[iMarker] = 0.0;
6772  Surface_MassFlow_Abs[iMarker] = 0.0;
6773 
6774  if (config->GetMarker_All_Analyze(iMarker) == YES) {
6775 
6776  for (iVertex = 0; iVertex < geometry->nVertex[iMarker]; iVertex++) {
6777  iPoint = geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNode();
6778 
6779  if (geometry->nodes->GetDomain(iPoint)) {
6780 
6781  geometry->vertex[iMarker][iVertex]->GetNormal(Vector);
6782 
6783  if (axisymmetric) {
6784  if (geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 1) != 0.0)
6785  AxiFactor = 2.0*PI_NUMBER*geometry->nodes->GetCoord(iPoint, 1);
6786  else
6787  AxiFactor = 1.0;
6788  } else {
6789  AxiFactor = 1.0;
6790  }
6791 
6792  Density = solver->GetNodes()->GetDensity(iPoint);
6793  Velocity2 = 0.0; Area = 0.0; MassFlow = 0.0; Vn = 0.0; Vtang2 = 0.0;
6794 
6795  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6796  Area += (Vector[iDim] * AxiFactor) * (Vector[iDim] * AxiFactor);
6797  Velocity[iDim] = solver->GetNodes()->GetVelocity(iPoint,iDim);
6798  Velocity2 += Velocity[iDim] * Velocity[iDim];
6799  Vn += Velocity[iDim] * Vector[iDim] * AxiFactor;
6800  MassFlow += Vector[iDim] * AxiFactor * Density * Velocity[iDim];
6801  }
6802 
6803  Area = sqrt (Area);
6804  if (AxiFactor == 0.0) Vn = 0.0; else Vn /= Area;
6805  Vn2 = Vn * Vn;
6806  Pressure = solver->GetNodes()->GetPressure(iPoint);
6807  SoundSpeed = solver->GetNodes()->GetSoundSpeed(iPoint);
6808 
6809  for (iDim = 0; iDim < nDim; iDim++) {
6810  TangVel[iDim] = Velocity[iDim] - Vn*Vector[iDim]*AxiFactor/Area;
6811  Vtang2 += TangVel[iDim]*TangVel[iDim];
6812  }
6813 
6814  if (incompressible){
6815  if (config->GetKind_DensityModel() == INC_DENSITYMODEL::VARIABLE) {
6816  Mach = sqrt(solver->GetNodes()->GetVelocity2(iPoint))/
6817  sqrt(solver->GetNodes()->GetSpecificHeatCp(iPoint)*config->GetPressure_ThermodynamicND()/(solver->GetNodes()->GetSpecificHeatCv(iPoint)*solver->GetNodes()->GetDensity(iPoint)));
6818  } else {
6819  Mach = sqrt(solver->GetNodes()->GetVelocity2(iPoint))/
6820  sqrt(config->GetBulk_Modulus()/(solver->GetNodes()->GetDensity(iPoint)));
6821  }
6822  Temperature = solver->GetNodes()->GetTemperature(iPoint);
6823  Enthalpy = solver->GetNodes()->GetSpecificHeatCp(iPoint)*Temperature;
6824  TotalTemperature = Temperature + 0.5*Velocity2/solver->GetNodes()->GetSpecificHeatCp(iPoint);
6825  TotalPressure = Pressure + 0.5*Density*Velocity2;
6826  }
6827  else{
6828  Mach = sqrt(Velocity2)/SoundSpeed;
6829  Temperature = Pressure / (Gas_Constant * Density);
6830  Enthalpy = solver->GetNodes()->GetEnthalpy(iPoint);
6831  TotalTemperature = Temperature * (1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0));
6832  TotalPressure = Pressure * pow( 1.0 + Mach * Mach * 0.5 * (Gamma - 1.0), Gamma / (Gamma - 1.0));
6833  }
6834 
6835  /*--- Compute the mass Surface_MassFlow ---*/
6836 
6837  Surface_Area[iMarker] += Area;
6838  Surface_MassFlow[iMarker] += MassFlow;
6839  Surface_MassFlow_Abs[iMarker] += abs(MassFlow);
6840 
6841  if (Kind_Average == AVERAGE_MASSFLUX) Weight = abs(MassFlow);
6842  else if (Kind_Average == AVERAGE_AREA) Weight = abs(Area);
6843  else Weight = 1.0;
6844 
6845  Surface_Mach[iMarker] += Mach*Weight;
6846  Surface_Temperature[iMarker] += Temperature*Weight;
6847  Surface_Density[iMarker] += Density*Weight;
6848  Surface_Enthalpy[iMarker] += Enthalpy*Weight;
6849  Surface_NormalVelocity[iMarker] += Vn*Weight;
6850  Surface_Pressure[iMarker] += Pressure*Weight;
6851  Surface_TotalTemperature[iMarker] += TotalTemperature*Weight;
6852  Surface_TotalPressure[iMarker] += TotalPressure*Weight;
6853 
6854  /*--- For now, always used the area to weight the uniformities. ---*/
6855 
6856  Weight = abs(Area);
6857 
6858  Surface_StreamVelocity2[iMarker] += Vn2*Weight;
6859  Surface_TransvVelocity2[iMarker] += Vtang2*Weight;
6860 
6861  }
6862  }
6863 
6864  }
6865 
6866  }
6867 
6868  /*--- Copy to the appropriate structure ---*/
6869 
6870  su2double *Surface_MassFlow_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6871  su2double *Surface_Mach_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6872  su2double *Surface_Temperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6873  su2double *Surface_Density_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6874  su2double *Surface_Enthalpy_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6875  su2double *Surface_NormalVelocity_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6876  su2double *Surface_StreamVelocity2_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6877  su2double *Surface_TransvVelocity2_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6878  su2double *Surface_Pressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6879  su2double *Surface_TotalTemperature_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6880  su2double *Surface_TotalPressure_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6881  su2double *Surface_Area_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6882  su2double *Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Local = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6883 
6884  su2double *Surface_MassFlow_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6885  su2double *Surface_Mach_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6886  su2double *Surface_Temperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6887  su2double *Surface_Density_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6888  su2double *Surface_Enthalpy_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6889  su2double *Surface_NormalVelocity_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6890  su2double *Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6891  su2double *Surface_TransvVelocity2_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6892  su2double *Surface_Pressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6893  su2double *Surface_TotalTemperature_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6894  su2double *Surface_TotalPressure_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6895  su2double *Surface_Area_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6896  su2double *Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6897 
6898  su2double *Surface_MomentumDistortion_Total = new su2double [nMarker_Analyze];
6899 
6900  for (iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
6901  Surface_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6902  Surface_Mach_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6903  Surface_Temperature_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6904  Surface_Density_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6905  Surface_Enthalpy_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6906  Surface_NormalVelocity_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6907  Surface_StreamVelocity2_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6908  Surface_TransvVelocity2_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6909  Surface_Pressure_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6910  Surface_TotalTemperature_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6911  Surface_TotalPressure_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6912  Surface_Area_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6913  Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Local[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6914 
6915  Surface_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6916  Surface_Mach_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6917  Surface_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6918  Surface_Density_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6919  Surface_Enthalpy_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6920  Surface_NormalVelocity_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6921  Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6922  Surface_TransvVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6923  Surface_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6924  Surface_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6925  Surface_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6926  Surface_Area_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6927  Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6928 
6929  Surface_MomentumDistortion_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
6930 
6931  }
6932 
6933  /*--- Compute the numerical fan face Mach number, mach number, temperature and the total area ---*/
6934 
6935  for (iMarker = 0; iMarker < config->GetnMarker_All(); iMarker++) {
6936 
6937  if (config->GetMarker_All_Analyze(iMarker) == YES) {
6938 
6939  for (iMarker_Analyze= 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
6940 
6941  /*--- Add the Surface_MassFlow, and Surface_Area to the particular boundary ---*/
6942 
6943  if (config->GetMarker_All_TagBound(iMarker) == config->GetMarker_Analyze_TagBound(iMarker_Analyze)) {
6944  Surface_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_MassFlow[iMarker];
6945  Surface_Mach_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_Mach[iMarker];
6946  Surface_Temperature_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_Temperature[iMarker];
6947  Surface_Density_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_Density[iMarker];
6948  Surface_Enthalpy_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_Enthalpy[iMarker];
6949  Surface_NormalVelocity_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_NormalVelocity[iMarker];
6950  Surface_StreamVelocity2_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_StreamVelocity2[iMarker];
6951  Surface_TransvVelocity2_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_TransvVelocity2[iMarker];
6952  Surface_Pressure_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_Pressure[iMarker];
6953  Surface_TotalTemperature_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_TotalTemperature[iMarker];
6954  Surface_TotalPressure_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_TotalPressure[iMarker];
6955  Surface_Area_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_Area[iMarker];
6956  Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Local[iMarker_Analyze] += Surface_MassFlow_Abs[iMarker];
6957  }
6958 
6959  }
6960 
6961  }
6962 
6963  }
6964 
6965 #ifdef HAVE_MPI
6966  if (config->GetComm_Level() == COMM_FULL) {
6967  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_MassFlow_Local, Surface_MassFlow_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6968  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_Mach_Local, Surface_Mach_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6969  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_Temperature_Local, Surface_Temperature_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6970  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_Density_Local, Surface_Density_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6971  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_Enthalpy_Local, Surface_Enthalpy_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6972  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_NormalVelocity_Local, Surface_NormalVelocity_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6973  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_StreamVelocity2_Local, Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6974  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_TransvVelocity2_Local, Surface_TransvVelocity2_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6975  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_Pressure_Local, Surface_Pressure_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6976  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_TotalTemperature_Local, Surface_TotalTemperature_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6977  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_TotalPressure_Local, Surface_TotalPressure_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6978  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_Area_Local, Surface_Area_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6979  SU2_MPI::Allreduce(Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Local, Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Total, nMarker_Analyze, MPI_DOUBLE, MPI_SUM, SU2_MPI::GetComm());
6980  }
6981 #else
6982 
6983  for (iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
6984  Surface_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_MassFlow_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6985  Surface_Mach_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_Mach_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6986  Surface_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_Temperature_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6987  Surface_Density_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_Density_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6988  Surface_Enthalpy_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_Enthalpy_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6989  Surface_NormalVelocity_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_NormalVelocity_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6990  Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_StreamVelocity2_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6991  Surface_TransvVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_TransvVelocity2_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6992  Surface_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_Pressure_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6993  Surface_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_TotalTemperature_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6994  Surface_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_TotalPressure_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6995  Surface_Area_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_Area_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6996  Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Local[iMarker_Analyze];
6997  }
6998 
6999 #endif
7000 
7001  /*--- Compute the value of Surface_Area_Total, and Surface_Pressure_Total, and
7002  set the value in the config structure for future use ---*/
7003 
7004  for (iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
7005 
7006  if (Kind_Average == AVERAGE_MASSFLUX) Weight = Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Total[iMarker_Analyze];
7007  else if (Kind_Average == AVERAGE_AREA) Weight = abs(Surface_Area_Total[iMarker_Analyze]);
7008  else Weight = 1.0;
7009 
7010  if (Weight != 0.0) {
7011  Surface_Mach_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
7012  Surface_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
7013  Surface_Density_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
7014  Surface_Enthalpy_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
7015  Surface_NormalVelocity_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
7016  Surface_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
7017  Surface_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
7018  Surface_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Weight;
7019  }
7020  else {
7021  Surface_Mach_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
7022  Surface_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
7023  Surface_Density_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
7024  Surface_Enthalpy_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
7025  Surface_NormalVelocity_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
7026  Surface_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
7027  Surface_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
7028  Surface_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
7029  }
7030 
7031  /*--- Compute flow uniformity parameters separately (always area for now). ---*/
7032 
7033  Area = fabs(Surface_Area_Total[iMarker_Analyze]);
7034 
7035  if (Area != 0.0) {
7036  Surface_MomentumDistortion_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze]/(Surface_NormalVelocity_Total[iMarker_Analyze]*Surface_NormalVelocity_Total[iMarker_Analyze]*Area) - 1.0;
7037  Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Area;
7038  Surface_TransvVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze] /= Area;
7039  }
7040  else {
7041  Surface_MomentumDistortion_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
7042  Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
7043  Surface_TransvVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze] = 0.0;
7044  }
7045 
7046  }
7047 
7048  for (iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
7049 
7050  su2double MassFlow = Surface_MassFlow_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetDensity_Ref() * config->GetVelocity_Ref();
7051  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) MassFlow *= 32.174;
7052  config->SetSurface_MassFlow(iMarker_Analyze, MassFlow);
7053 
7054  su2double Mach = Surface_Mach_Total[iMarker_Analyze];
7055  config->SetSurface_Mach(iMarker_Analyze, Mach);
7056 
7057  su2double Temperature = Surface_Temperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetTemperature_Ref();
7058  config->SetSurface_Temperature(iMarker_Analyze, Temperature);
7059 
7060  su2double Pressure = Surface_Pressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetPressure_Ref();
7061  config->SetSurface_Pressure(iMarker_Analyze, Pressure);
7062 
7063  su2double Density = Surface_Density_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetDensity_Ref();
7064  config->SetSurface_Density(iMarker_Analyze, Density);
7065 
7066  su2double Enthalpy = Surface_Enthalpy_Total[iMarker_Analyze];
7067  config->SetSurface_Enthalpy(iMarker_Analyze, Enthalpy);
7068 
7069  su2double NormalVelocity = Surface_NormalVelocity_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetVelocity_Ref();
7070  config->SetSurface_NormalVelocity(iMarker_Analyze, NormalVelocity);
7071 
7072  su2double Uniformity = sqrt(Surface_StreamVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze]) * config->GetVelocity_Ref();
7073  config->SetSurface_Uniformity(iMarker_Analyze, Uniformity);
7074 
7075  su2double SecondaryStrength = sqrt(Surface_TransvVelocity2_Total[iMarker_Analyze]) * config->GetVelocity_Ref();
7076  config->SetSurface_SecondaryStrength(iMarker_Analyze, SecondaryStrength);
7077 
7078  su2double MomentumDistortion = Surface_MomentumDistortion_Total[iMarker_Analyze];
7079  config->SetSurface_MomentumDistortion(iMarker_Analyze, MomentumDistortion);
7080 
7081  su2double SecondOverUniform = SecondaryStrength/Uniformity;
7082  config->SetSurface_SecondOverUniform(iMarker_Analyze, SecondOverUniform);
7083 
7084  su2double TotalTemperature = Surface_TotalTemperature_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetTemperature_Ref();
7085  config->SetSurface_TotalTemperature(iMarker_Analyze, TotalTemperature);
7086 
7087  su2double TotalPressure = Surface_TotalPressure_Total[iMarker_Analyze] * config->GetPressure_Ref();
7088  config->SetSurface_TotalPressure(iMarker_Analyze, TotalPressure);
7089 
7090  }
7091 
7092  /*--- Compute the average static pressure drop between two surfaces. Note
7093  that this assumes we have two surfaces being analyzed and that the outlet
7094  is first followed by the inlet. This is because we may also want to choose
7095  outlet values (temperature, uniformity, etc.) for our design problems,
7096  which require the outlet to be listed first. This is a simple first version
7097  that could be generalized to a different orders/lists/etc. ---*/
7098 
7099  for (iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
7100  if (nMarker_Analyze == 2) {
7101  su2double Pressure_Drop = (Surface_Pressure_Total[1]-Surface_Pressure_Total[0]) * config->GetPressure_Ref();
7102  config->SetSurface_PressureDrop(iMarker_Analyze, Pressure_Drop);
7103  } else {
7104  config->SetSurface_PressureDrop(iMarker_Analyze, 0.0);
7105  }
7106  }
7107 
7108  if ((rank == MASTER_NODE) && !config->GetDiscrete_Adjoint() && output) {
7109 
7110  cout.precision(6);
7111  cout.setf(ios::scientific, ios::floatfield);
7112  cout << endl << "Computing surface mean values." << endl << endl;
7113 
7114  for (iMarker_Analyze = 0; iMarker_Analyze < nMarker_Analyze; iMarker_Analyze++) {
7115  cout << "Surface "<< config->GetMarker_Analyze_TagBound(iMarker_Analyze) << ":" << endl;
7116 
7117  if (nDim == 3) { if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setw(20) << "Area (m^2): "; else cout << setw(20) << "Area (ft^2): "; }
7118  else { if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setw(20) << "Area (m): "; else cout << setw(20) << "Area (ft): "; }
7119 
7120  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setw(15) << fabs(Surface_Area_Total[iMarker_Analyze]);
7121  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setw(15) << fabs(Surface_Area_Total[iMarker_Analyze])*12.0*12.0;
7122 
7123  cout << endl;
7124 
7125  su2double MassFlow = config->GetSurface_MassFlow(iMarker_Analyze);
7126  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setw(20) << "Mf (kg/s): " << setw(15) << MassFlow;
7127  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setw(20) << "Mf (lbs/s): " << setw(15) << MassFlow;
7128 
7129  su2double NormalVelocity = config->GetSurface_NormalVelocity(iMarker_Analyze);
7130  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setw(20) << "Vn (m/s): " << setw(15) << NormalVelocity;
7131  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setw(20) << "Vn (ft/s): " << setw(15) << NormalVelocity;
7132 
7133  cout << endl;
7134 
7135  su2double Uniformity = config->GetSurface_Uniformity(iMarker_Analyze);
7136  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setw(20) << "Uniformity (m/s): " << setw(15) << Uniformity;
7137  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setw(20) << "Uniformity (ft/s): " << setw(15) << Uniformity;
7138 
7139  su2double SecondaryStrength = config->GetSurface_SecondaryStrength(iMarker_Analyze);
7140  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setw(20) << "Secondary (m/s): " << setw(15) << SecondaryStrength;
7141  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setw(20) << "Secondary (ft/s): " << setw(15) << SecondaryStrength;
7142 
7143  cout << endl;
7144 
7145  su2double MomentumDistortion = config->GetSurface_MomentumDistortion(iMarker_Analyze);
7146  cout << setw(20) << "Mom. Distortion: " << setw(15) << MomentumDistortion;
7147 
7148  su2double SecondOverUniform = config->GetSurface_SecondOverUniform(iMarker_Analyze);
7149  cout << setw(20) << "Second/Uniform: " << setw(15) << SecondOverUniform;
7150 
7151  cout << endl;
7152 
7153  su2double Pressure = config->GetSurface_Pressure(iMarker_Analyze);
7154  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setw(20) << "P (Pa): " << setw(15) << Pressure;
7155  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setw(20) << "P (psf): " << setw(15) << Pressure;
7156 
7157  su2double TotalPressure = config->GetSurface_TotalPressure(iMarker_Analyze);
7158  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setw(20) << "PT (Pa): " << setw(15) <<TotalPressure;
7159  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setw(20) << "PT (psf): " << setw(15) <<TotalPressure;
7160 
7161  cout << endl;
7162 
7163  su2double Mach = config->GetSurface_Mach(iMarker_Analyze);
7164  cout << setw(20) << "Mach: " << setw(15) << Mach;
7165 
7166  su2double Density = config->GetSurface_Density(iMarker_Analyze);
7167  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setw(20) << "Rho (kg/m^3): " << setw(15) << Density;
7168  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setw(20) << "Rho (lb/ft^3): " << setw(15) << Density*32.174;
7169 
7170  cout << endl;
7171 
7172  if (compressible || energy) {
7173  su2double Temperature = config->GetSurface_Temperature(iMarker_Analyze);
7174  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setw(20) << "T (K): " << setw(15) << Temperature;
7175  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setw(20) << "T (R): " << setw(15) << Temperature;
7176 
7177  su2double TotalTemperature = config->GetSurface_TotalTemperature(iMarker_Analyze);
7178  if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == SI) cout << setw(20) << "TT (K): " << setw(15) << TotalTemperature;
7179  else if (config->GetSystemMeasurements() == US) cout << setw(20) << "TT (R): " << setw(15) << TotalTemperature;
7180 
7181  cout << endl;
7182  }
7183 
7184  }
7185  cout.unsetf(ios_base::floatfield);
7186 
7187  }
7188 
7189  delete [] Surface_MassFlow_Local;
7190  delete [] Surface_Mach_Local;
7191  delete [] Surface_Temperature_Local;
7192  delete [] Surface_Density_Local;
7193  delete [] Surface_Enthalpy_Local;
7194  delete [] Surface_NormalVelocity_Local;
7195  delete [] Surface_Pressure_Local;
7196  delete [] Surface_TotalTemperature_Local;
7197  delete [] Surface_TotalPressure_Local;
7198  delete [] Surface_Area_Local;
7199  delete [] Surface_MassFlow_Abs_Local;
7200 
7201  delete [] Surface_MassFlow_Total;
7202  delete [] Surface_Mach_Total;
